<h2 data-section-id="zofl7" data-start="93" data-end="111">🎯 What is KPI?</h2>
<p data-start="113" data-end="148"><strong data-start="113" data-end="148">KPI = Key Performance Indicator</strong></p>
<p data-start="150" data-end="226">👉 It is a <strong data-start="161" data-end="181">measurable value</strong> that shows how well something is performing.</p>
<p data-start="228" data-end="344">Think of it like a <strong data-start="247" data-end="274">scoreboard in a game 🎮</strong><br data-start="274" data-end="277">
You don’t just play… you check the score to know if you’re winning.</p>
<hr data-start="346" data-end="349">
<h2 data-section-id="d9svfw" data-start="351" data-end="372">💡 Simple Examples</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1cxf1vo" data-start="374" data-end="390">📊 In Sales:</h3>
<ul data-start="391" data-end="438">
<li data-section-id="lkiyma" data-start="391" data-end="406">
<p data-start="393" data-end="406">Total Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1f7why6" data-start="407" data-end="417">
<p data-start="409" data-end="417">Profit</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lycen3" data-start="418" data-end="438">
<p data-start="420" data-end="438">Number of Orders</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="440" data-end="517">👉 These are KPIs because they tell:<br>
<strong data-start="477" data-end="517">“Is the business doing well or not?”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="519" data-end="522">
<h3 data-section-id="1x78jy1" data-start="524" data-end="540">👩‍💼 In HR:</h3>
<ul data-start="541" data-end="601">
<li data-section-id="z7atm6" data-start="541" data-end="568">
<p data-start="543" data-end="568">Employee Attrition Rate</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1p24vhm" data-start="569" data-end="585">
<p data-start="571" data-end="585">Attendance %</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="e2ntla" data-start="586" data-end="601">
<p data-start="588" data-end="601">Hiring Time</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="603" data-end="606">
<h3 data-section-id="1n5rgdg" data-start="608" data-end="640">📈 In Data Analyst Projects:</h3>
<p data-start="641" data-end="653">Common KPIs:</p>
<ul data-start="654" data-end="716">
<li data-section-id="1w5mi1e" data-start="654" data-end="665">
<p data-start="656" data-end="665">Revenue</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wm5znk" data-start="666" data-end="683">
<p data-start="668" data-end="683">Profit Margin</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mmv3q4" data-start="684" data-end="696">
<p data-start="686" data-end="696">Growth %</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18a9mj6" data-start="697" data-end="716">
<p data-start="699" data-end="716">Conversion Rate</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="718" data-end="721">
<h2 data-section-id="1bglygo" data-start="723" data-end="751">🧠 One-Line Understanding</h2>
<p data-start="753" data-end="805">👉 <strong data-start="756" data-end="805">KPI = Important number that shows performance</strong></p>
<hr data-start="807" data-end="810">
<h2 data-section-id="1d7u642" data-start="812" data-end="850">🔥 Example (Very Important for You)</h2>
<p data-start="852" data-end="904">If you make a <strong data-start="866" data-end="885">Sales Dashboard</strong>, your KPIs can be:</p>
<ul data-start="906" data-end="981">
<li data-section-id="17c92xd" data-start="906" data-end="935">
<p data-start="908" data-end="935">Total Revenue = ₹5,00,000</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15gr6px" data-start="936" data-end="960">
<p data-start="938" data-end="960">Total Orders = 1,200</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pwzmmm" data-start="961" data-end="981">
<p data-start="963" data-end="981">Profit = ₹80,000</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="983" data-end="1034">👉 These numbers at the top of dashboard = <strong data-start="1026" data-end="1034">KPIs</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1036" data-end="1039">
<h2 data-section-id="9fvhm3" data-start="1041" data-end="1071">⚡ Pro Tip (Interview Trick)</h2>
<p data-start="1073" data-end="1121">If interviewer asks:<br>
👉 “What KPIs did you use?”</p>
<p data-start="1123" data-end="1240">You say:<br>
👉 “I used KPIs like revenue, profit, and order count to evaluate business performance and identify trends.”</p>
<p data-start="1242" data-end="1269">💥 This sounds professional</p>
<hr data-start="1271" data-end="1274">
<p data-start="1276" data-end="1417" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want, I can next:<br>
✅ Show you <strong data-start="1312" data-end="1360">how to create KPI cards in Excel or Power BI</strong><br data-start="1360" data-end="1363">
✅ Or give you a <strong data-start="1379" data-end="1414">real project with KPIs included</strong> 🚀</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#2126ae" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Share" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#630ca2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary touch:w-10 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" aria-label="More actions" type="button" id="radix-_r_vv_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#f6d0e2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-(--header-height)" dir="auto" data-turn-id="cf300ed5-c4bc-4065-8c04-c474b6c8e534" data-testid="conversation-turn-19" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thre