oken-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-WEB:7db6c802-7c43-47fb-9316-1a3dfc040aaa-33" data-testid="conversation-turn-22" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant" style=""><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="eb559ea3-becc-419d-a8e2-e1dbc4c9adfb" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="30">First, your corrected version:</p>
<p data-start="32" data-end="304"><strong data-start="32" data-end="304">“KPIs are calculated columns made from raw data. They are like other columns but show valuable results. For example, I have three columns: Name, First Month Salary, and Second Month Salary. Then I create a fourth column with total salary. Is this fourth column a KPI?”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="306" data-end="309">
<p data-start="311" data-end="374">Now let’s clear this properly (this is an important concept) 👇</p>
<h2 data-section-id="o241v1" data-start="376" data-end="440"><span role="text">⚠️ Your understanding is <strong data-start="404" data-end="425">partially correct</strong>, but not fully</span></h2>
<p data-start="442" data-end="485">👉 The <strong data-start="449" data-end="481">fourth column (Total Salary)</strong> is:</p>
<p data-start="487" data-end="540">✅ A <strong data-start="491" data-end="512">calculated column</strong><br data-start="512" data-end="515">
❌ <strong data-start="517" data-end="540">NOT a KPI (usually)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="542" data-end="545">
<h2 data-section-id="rk5i6a" data-start="547" data-end="557">🧠 Why?</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="4y94rg" data-start="559" data-end="579">📄 Your Example:</h3>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="581" data-end="693" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="581" data-end="638"><tr data-start="581" data-end="638"><th data-start="581" data-end="588" data-col-size="sm" class="">Name</th><th data-start="588" data-end="605" data-col-size="sm" class="">Month 1 Salary</th><th data-start="605" data-end="622" data-col-size="sm" class="">Month 2 Salary</th><th data-start="622" data-end="638" data-col-size="sm" class="">Total Salary</th></tr></thead></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="695" data-end="721">👉 “Total Salary” here is:</p>
<ul data-start="722" data-end="768">
<li data-section-id="1wyv37y" data-start="722" data-end="746">
<p data-start="724" data-end="746">Row-wise calculation</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1d7ic4e" data-start="747" data-end="768">
<p data-start="749" data-end="768">For each employee</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="770" data-end="801">➡️ This = <strong data-start="780" data-end="801">calculated column</strong></p>
<hr data-start="803" data-end="806">
<h2 data-section-id="4o87d4" data-start="808" data-end="839">🎯 What WOULD be a KPI here?</h2>
<p data-start="841" data-end="865">A KPI is something like:</p>
<ul data-start="867" data-end="950">
<li data-section-id="do9gyv" data-start="867" data-end="904">
<p data-start="869" data-end="904"><strong data-start="869" data-end="902">Total Salary of all employees</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17rcrhb" data-start="905" data-end="927">
<p data-start="907" data-end="927"><strong data-start="907" data-end="925">Average Salary</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="146za4w" data-start="928" data-end="950">
<p data-start="930" data-end="950"><strong data-start="930" data-end="948">Highest Salary</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="952" data-end="965">👉 These are:</p>
<ul data-start="966" data-end="1052">
<li data-section-id="1onzegs" data-start="966" data-end="984">
<p data-start="968" data-end="984">Summary values</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6cq9s" data-start="985" data-end="1020">
<p data-start="987" data-end="1020">One number (or few key numbers)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gwapo4" data-start="1021" data-end="1052">
<p data-start="1023" data-end="1052">Used to measure performance</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1054" data-end="1057">
<h2 data-section-id="13ingxl" data-start="1059" data-end="1092">💡 Simple Rule (Remember this)</h2>
<p data-start="1094" data-end="1188">👉 <strong data-start="1097" data-end="1143">Calculated Column = row level (per record)</strong><br data-start="1143" data-end="1146">
👉 <strong data-start="1149" data-end="1188">KPI = overall summary (big picture)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1190" data-end="1193">
<h2 data-section-id="luyu5m" data-start="1195" data-end="1216">🔥 Easy Comparison</h2>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="1218" data-end="1366" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="1218" data-end="1236"><tr data-start="1218" data-end="1236"><th data-start="1218" data-end="1225" data-col-size="sm" class="">Type</th><th data-start="1225" data-end="1236" data-col-size="sm" class="">Example</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="1255" data-end="1366"><tr data-start="1255" data-end="1274"><td data-start="1255" data-end="1264" data-col-size="sm">Column</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="1264" data-end="1274">Salary</td></tr><tr data-start="1275" data-end="1322"><td data-start="1275" data-end="1295" data-col-size="sm">Calculated Column</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="1295" data-end="1322">Total Salary per person</td></tr><tr data-start="1323" data-end="1366"><td data-start="1323" data-end="1329" data-col-size="sm">KPI</td><td data-start="1329" data-end="1366" data-col-size="sm">Total company salary / Avg salary</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="1368" data-end="1371">
<h2 data-section-id="jj3vl6" data-start="1373" data-end="1394">🎮 Think Like This</h2>
<ul data-start="1396" data-end="1488">
<li data-section-id="pm4t8w" data-start="1396" data-end="1417">
<p data-start="1398" data-end="1417">Columns = players</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2t9ne9" data-start="1418" data-end="1454">
<p data-start="1420" data-end="1454">Calculated column = player stats</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12v8g3" data-start="1455" data-end="1488">
<p data-start="1457" data-end="1488">KPI = <strong data-start="1463" data-end="1483">final scoreboard</strong> 🏆</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1490" data-end="1493">
<h2 data-section-id="7cwyd0" data-start="1495" data-end="1512">⚡ Final Answer</h2>
<p data-start="1514" data-end="1629">👉 ❌ Your 4th column = KPI → No<br data-start="1545" data-end="1548">
👉 ✅ It is a <strong data-start="1561" data-end="1582">calculated column</strong><br data-start="1582" data-end="1585">
👉 ✅ KPI = summary like total, average, etc.</p>
<hr data-start="1631" data-end="1634">
<p data-start="1636" data-end="1791" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want, next I can:<br>
✅ Show you <strong data-start="1672" data-end="1728">how to create KPI in Excel + Power BI (step-by-step)</strong><br data-start="1728" data-end="1731">
✅ Or give you a <strong data-start="1747" data-end="1788">mini project to practice this concept</strong> 🚀</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pr