<p data-start="33" data-end="86"><strong data-start="33" data-end="86">“Give me a table and identify what the KPIs are.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="88" data-end="91">
<p data-start="93" data-end="137">Now let’s learn this in a super clear way 👇</p>
<h2 data-section-id="wmhvqs" data-start="139" data-end="162">📄 Sample Data Table</h2>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="164" data-end="510" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="164" data-end="225"><tr data-start="164" data-end="225"><th data-start="164" data-end="175" data-col-size="sm" class="">Employee</th><th data-start="175" data-end="192" data-col-size="sm" class="">Month 1 Salary</th><th data-start="192" data-end="209" data-col-size="sm" class="">Month 2 Salary</th><th data-start="209" data-end="225" data-col-size="sm" class="">Total Salary</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="283" data-end="510"><tr data-start="283" data-end="339"><td data-start="283" data-end="294" data-col-size="sm">A</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="294" data-end="309">20,000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="309" data-end="324">22,000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="324" data-end="339">42,000</td></tr><tr data-start="340" data-end="396"><td data-start="340" data-end="351" data-col-size="sm">B</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="351" data-end="366">25,000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="366" data-end="381">24,000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="381" data-end="396">49,000</td></tr><tr data-start="397" data-end="453"><td data-start="397" data-end="408" data-col-size="sm">C</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="408" data-end="423">18,000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="423" data-end="438">20,000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="438" data-end="453">38,000</td></tr><tr data-start="454" data-end="510"><td data-start="454" data-end="465" data-col-size="sm">D</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="465" data-end="480">30,000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="480" data-end="495">28,000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="495" data-end="510">58,000</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 