<p data-start="33" data-end="96"><strong data-start="33" data-end="96">“So, as we decided, let’s create one strong Excel project.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="98" data-end="101">
<p data-start="103" data-end="172">Perfect. Now we build something that actually gets you shortlisted 🚀</p>
<h2 data-section-id="wo2tp7" data-start="174" data-end="235"><span role="text">🎯 Your Project 1: <strong data-start="196" data-end="235">Sales Performance Dashboard (Excel)</strong></span></h2>
<p data-start="237" data-end="298">This is beginner-friendly BUT powerful enough for interviews.</p>
<hr data-start="300" data-end="303">
<h2 data-section-id="2yuign" data-start="305" data-end="354">📦 Step 1: Your Dataset (Create this in Excel)</h2>
<p data-start="356" data-end="373">Paste this table:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="375" data-end="904" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="375" data-end="427"><tr data-start="375" data-end="427"><th data-start="375" data-end="388" data-col-size="sm" class="">Order Date</th><th data-start="388" data-end="397" data-col-size="sm" class="">Region</th><th data-start="397" data-end="407" data-col-size="sm" class="">Product</th><th data-start="407" data-end="415" data-col-size="sm" class="">Sales</th><th data-start="415" data-end="427" data-col-size="sm" class="">Quantity</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="481" data-end="904"><tr data-start="481" data-end="533"><td data-start="481" data-end="494" data-col-size="sm">01-Jan</td><td data-start="494" data-end="503" data-col-size="sm">North</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="503" data-end="513">Laptop</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="513" data-end="521">50000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="521" data-end="533">2</td></tr><tr data-start="534" data-end="586"><td data-start="534" data-end="547" data-col-size="sm">02-Jan</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="547" data-end="556">South</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="556" data-end="566">Mobile</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="566" data-end="574">20000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="574" data-end="586">5</td></tr><tr data-start="587" data-end="639"><td data-start="587" data-end="600" data-col-size="sm">03-Jan</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="600" data-end="609">East</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="609" data-end="619">Tablet</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="619" data-end="627">15000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="627" data-end="639">3</td></tr><tr data-start="640" data-end="692"><td data-start="640" data-end="653" data-col-size="sm">04-Jan</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="653" data-end="662">West</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="662" data-end="672">Laptop</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="672" data-end="680">55000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="680" data-end="692">2</td></tr><tr data-start="693" data-end="745"><td data-start="693" data-end="706" data-col-size="sm">05-Jan</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="706" data-end="715">North</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="715" data-end="725">Mobile</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="725" data-end="733">22000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="733" data-end="745">4</td></tr><tr data-start="746" data-end="798"><td data-start="746" data-end="759" data-col-size="sm">06-Jan</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="759" data-end="768">South</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="768" data-end="778">Tablet</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="778" data-end="786">12000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="786" data-end="798">2</td></tr><tr data-start="799" data-end="851"><td data-start="799" data-end="812" data-col-size="sm">07-Jan</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="812" data-end="821">East</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="821" data-end="831">Laptop</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="831" data-end="839">60000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="839" data-end="851">3</td></tr><tr data-start="852" data-end="904"><td data-start="852" data-end="865" data-col-size="sm">08-Jan</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="865" data-end="874">West</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="874" data-end="884">Mobile</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="884" data-end="892">25000</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="892" data-end="904">6</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="906" data-end="945">👉 (You can extend to 20–30 rows later)</p>
<hr data-start="947" data-end="950">
<h2 data-section-id="1twvfs7" data-start="952" data-end="991">🧠 Step 2: Create KPIs (Top Section)</h2>
<p data-start="993" data-end="1006">Create these:</p>
<ul data-start="1008" data-end="1187">
<li data-section-id="biavp5" data-start="1008" data-end="1050">
<p data-start="1010" data-end="1050"><strong data-start="1010" data-end="1025">Total Sales</strong> → <code data-start="1028" data-end="1048">=SUM(Sales column)</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="r15uop" data-start="1051" data-end="1099">
<p data-start="1053" data-end="1099"><strong data-start="1053" data-end="1071">Total Quantity</strong> → <code data-start="1074" data-end="1097">=SUM(Quantity column)</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o7k2wg" data-start="1100" data-end="1148">
<p data-start="1102" data-end="1148"><strong data-start="1102" data-end="1119">Average Sales</strong> → <code data-start="1122" data-end="1146">=AVERAGE(Sales column)</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lacxww" data-start="1149" data-end="1187">
<p data-start="1151" data-end="1187"><strong data-start="1151" data-end="1164">Max Sales</strong> → <code data-start="1167" data-end="1187">=MAX(Sales column)</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1189" data-end="1229">👉 These will be your <strong data-start="1211" data-end="1229">dashboard KPIs</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1231" data-end="1234">
<h2 data-section-id="k0tzi3" data-start="1236" data-end="1275">📊 Step 3: Pivot Tables (Core Skill)</h2>
<p data-start="1277" data-end="1297">Create Pivot Tables:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="16twmky" data-start="1299" data-end="1321">1. Sales by Region</h3>
<ul data-start="1322" data-end="1365">
<li data-section-id="87yyt7" data-start="1322" data-end="1339">
<p data-start="1324" data-end="1339">Rows → Region</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ph0weg" data-start="1340" data-end="1365">
<p data-start="1342" data-end="1365">Values → Sum of Sales</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1ai6pj6" data-start="1367" data-end="1390">2. Sales by Product</h3>
<ul data-start="1391" data-end="1435">
<li data-section-id="15dn53c" data-start="1391" data-end="1409">
<p data-start="1393" data-end="1409">Rows → Product</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ph0weg" data-start="1410" data-end="1435">
<p data-start="1412" data-end="1435">Values → Sum of Sales</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1437" data-end="1440">
<h2 data-section-id="18ttx03" data-start="1442" data-end="1462">📈 Step 4: Charts</h2>
<p data-start="1464" data-end="1471">Create:</p>
<ul data-start="1472" data-end="1536">
<li data-section-id="72n0gc" data-start="1472" data-end="1503">
<p data-start="1474" data-end="1503">Bar chart → Sales by Region</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19p006q" data-start="1504" data-end="1536">
<p data-start="1506" data-end="1536">Pie chart → Sales by Product</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1538" data-end="1541">
<h2 data-section-id="15fwjys" data-start="1543" data-end="1580">🎛️ Step 5: Add Slicer (Important)</h2>
<p data-start="1582" data-end="1597">Add slicer for:</p>
<ul data-start="1598" data-end="1620">
<li data-section-id="nj2lcg" data-start="1598" data-end="1608">
<p data-start="1600" data-end="1608">Region</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gybhab" data-start="1609" data-end="1620">
<p data-start="1611" data-end="1620">Product</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1622" data-end="1665">👉 This makes your dashboard interactive 💥</p>
<hr data-start="1667" data-end="1670">
<h2 data-section-id="1xtlf7q" data-start="1672" data-end="1706">🎨 Step 6: Make Dashboard Sheet</h2>
<ul data-start="1708" data-end="1825">
<li data-section-id="pjd54t" data-start="1708" data-end="1747">
<p data-start="1710" data-end="1747">Move all charts + KPIs to one sheet</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uxj4na" data-start="1748" data-end="1796">
<p data-start="1750" data-end="1796">Add title: <strong data-start="1761" data-end="1794">“Sales Performance Dashboard”</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="7ezqc4" data-start="1797" data-end="1825">
<p data-start="1799" data-end="1825">Align everything cleanly</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1827" data-end="1830">
<h2 data-section-id="1v22wmx" data-start="1832" data-end="1855">🔥 What You’ll Learn</h2>
<ul data-start="1857" data-end="1958">
<li data-section-id="1bnd5kt" data-start="1857" data-end="1874">
<p data-start="1859" data-end="1874">Data cleaning</p>
