ext-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="31">First, your corrected sentence:</p>
<p data-start="33" data-end="142"><strong data-start="33" data-end="142">“Is this a good file? Will recruiters find it impressive, or does it look like a beginner-level dataset?”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="144" data-end="147">
<p data-start="149" data-end="173">Now the honest answer 👇</p>
<h2 data-section-id="1gdk8g6" data-start="175" data-end="208">🧠 The Truth (No sugarcoating)</h2>
<p data-start="210" data-end="322">👉 The <strong data-start="217" data-end="245">data file itself is GOOD</strong><br data-start="245" data-end="248">
👉 But <strong data-start="255" data-end="322">recruiters don’t judge the file… they judge what YOU do with it</strong></p>
<p data-start="324" data-end="334">Right now:</p>
<ul data-start="336" data-end="418">
<li data-section-id="emsw9q" data-start="336" data-end="370">
<p data-start="338" data-end="370">📄 Dataset → looks realistic ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ym8y3l" data-start="371" data-end="418">
<p data-start="373" data-end="418">💼 Your project (not built yet) → unknown ❌</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="420" data-end="423">
<h2 data-section-id="1v5c5lo" data-start="425" data-end="454">🎯 Important Mindset Shift</h2>
<p data-start="456" data-end="482">Recruiter is NOT thinking:</p>
<blockquote data-start="483" data-end="507">
<p data-start="485" data-end="507">“Wow, nice Excel file”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="509" data-end="527">They are thinking:</p>
<blockquote data-start="528" data-end="579">
<p data-start="530" data-end="579">“Can this person analyze data and give insights?”</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="581" data-end="584">
<h2 data-section-id="1mjtm21" data-start="586" data-end="634">🔥 So what makes it look “BEGINNER” vs “PRO”?</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="t5mgw1" data-start="636" data-end="658">❌ Beginner Project</h3>
<ul data-start="659" data-end="729">
<li data-section-id="48b71l" data-start="659" data-end="680">
<p data-start="661" data-end="680">Just pivot tables</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="129cksv" data-start="681" data-end="696">
<p data-start="683" data-end="696">Just charts</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lk70e4" data-start="697" data-end="712">
<p data-start="699" data-end="712">No insights</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ye9k2r" data-start="713" data-end="729">
<p data-start="715" data-end="729">Messy layout</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="731" data-end="751">👉 This gets ignored</p>
<hr data-start="753" data-end="756">
<h3 data-section-id="ze5ytk" data-start="758" data-end="796">✅ Strong / Recruiter-Level Project</h3>
<ul data-start="797" data-end="906">
<li data-section-id="z72l6x" data-start="797" data-end="816">
<p data-start="799" data-end="816">Clean dashboard</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17sip37" data-start="817" data-end="832">
<p data-start="819" data-end="832">Proper KPIs</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hp0yz5" data-start="833" data-end="856">
<p data-start="835" data-end="856">Interactive slicers</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16y8bna" data-start="857" data-end="889">
<p data-start="859" data-end="889"><strong data-start="859" data-end="887">Insights written clearly</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13kmfuh" data-start="890" data-end="906">
<p data-start="892" data-end="906">Logical flow</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="908" data-end="935">👉 This gets shortlisted 💥</p>
<hr data-start="937" data-end="940">
<h2 data-section-id="10uq9vq" data-start="942" data-end="966">💡 Example Difference</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1606zmw" data-start="968" data-end="979">❌ Weak:</h3>
<p data-start="980" data-end="1017">“Created sales dashboard using Excel”</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1czowfe" data-start="1019" data-end="1032">✅ Strong:</h3>
<p data-start="1033" data-end="1163">“Identified that the West region contributes highest revenue (32%) and Mobile category drives maximum sales using Excel dashboard”</p>
<hr data-start="1165" data-end="1168">
<h2 data-section-id="f5yjfg" data-start="1170" data-end="1195">⚡ Your Dataset Verdict</h2>
<p data-start="1197" data-end="1286">👉 ❌ Not too basic<br data-start="1215" data-end="1218">
👉 ❌ Not too advanced<br data-start="1239" data-end="1242">
👉 ✅ Perfect for building a strong project</p>
<p data-start="1288" data-end="1292">BUT…</p>
<p data-start="1294" data-end="1373">👉 If you use it normally → beginner<br data-start="1330" data-end="1333">
👉 If you use it smartly → impressive 🔥</p>
<hr data-start="1375" data-end="1378">
<h2 data-section-id="a39rzq" data-start="1380" data-end="1411">🚀 How YOU make it stand out</h2>
<p data-start="1413" data-end="1431">Do these 3 things:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1okay9b" data-start="1433" data-end="1469">1. Add Insights (MOST IMPORTANT)</h3>
<p data-start="1470" data-end="1476">Write:</p>
<ul data-start="1477" data-end="1517">
<li data-section-id="19a4mhn" data-start="1477" data-end="1491">
<p data-start="1479" data-end="1491">Top region</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5imi94" data-start="1492" data-end="1507">
<p data-start="1494" data-end="1507">Top product</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11lbw0x" data-start="1508" data-end="1517">
<p data-start="1510" data-end="1517">Trend</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1519" data-end="1522">
<h3 data-section-id="is99zd" data-start="1524" data-end="1553">2. Clean Dashboard Design</h3>
<ul data-start="1554" data-end="1597">
<li data-section-id="nh8cir" data-start="1554" data-end="1572">
<p data-start="1556" data-end="1572">Proper spacing</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vfxtmj" data-start="1573" data-end="1583">
<p data-start="1575" data-end="1583">Titles</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wxqgt9" data-start="1584" data-end="1597">
<p data-start="1586" data-end="1597">KPI cards</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1599" data-end="1602">
<h3 data-section-id="ysmi68" data-start="1604" data-end="1626">3. Add Interaction</h3>
<ul data-start="1627" data-end="1650">
<li data-section-id="67a7o9" data-start="1627" data-end="1638">
<p data-start="1629" data-end="1638">Slicers</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12wvk0r" data-start="1639" data-end="1650">
<p data-start="1641" data-end="1650">Filters</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1652" data-end="1655">
<h2 data-section-id="5516lo" data-start="1657" data-end="1676">🧠 Final Verdict</h2>
<p data-start="1678" data-end="1724">👉 Dataset = tool<br data-start="1695" data-end="1698">
👉 Your analysis = value</p>
<hr data-start="1726" data-end="1729">
<p data-start="1731" data-end="1867">If you want next step, I can:<br>
✅ Tell you <strong data-start="1772" data-end="1819">exact layout of dashboard (like a template)</strong><br data-start="1819" data-end="1822">
✅ Or guide you step-by-step while you build</p>
<p data-start="1869" data-end="1911" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Just say:<br data-start="1878" data-end="1881">
<strong data-start="1881" data-end="1908">“guide me step by step”</strong> 🚀</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad