<h1 data-section-id="1jnu8yr" data-start="518" data-end="539">🎯 PROJECT OVERVIEW</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1njy4uy" data-start="541" data-end="560">📊 Project Name:</h2>
<p data-start="561" data-end="619"><strong data-start="561" data-end="619">Retail Sales Performance &amp; Customer Insights Dashboard</strong></p>
<hr data-start="621" data-end="624">
<h2 data-section-id="77iq1" data-start="626" data-end="665">🧠 Business Problem (VERY IMPORTANT)</h2>
<p data-start="667" data-end="704">Imagine you are working in a company.</p>
<p data-start="706" data-end="723">The manager asks:</p>
<p data-start="725" data-end="772">👉 “We have sales data, but I don’t understand:</p>
<ul data-start="773" data-end="933">
<li data-section-id="yin2cw" data-start="773" data-end="802">
<p data-start="775" data-end="802">Which region performs best?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fo6fh3" data-start="803" data-end="840">
