</li>
<li data-section-id="13dn830" data-start="841" data-end="888">
<p data-start="843" data-end="888">Are new or returning customers more valuable?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qgvvh5" data-start="889" data-end="933">
<p data-start="891" data-end="933">Where should we focus to increase profit?”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="935" data-end="981">👉 Your job = <strong data-start="949" data-end="981">turn raw data into decisions</strong></p>
