<h1 data-section-id="16b0t6g" data-start="1173" data-end="1215">🧭 COMPLETE WORKFLOW (Like Real Company)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="12i66ok" data-start="1217" data-end="1250">🔥 STEP 1: Understand Raw Data</h2>
<p data-start="1252" data-end="1288">Open file → Don’t touch anything yet</p>
<p data-start="1290" data-end="1296">Check:</p>
<ul data-start="1297" data-end="1382">
<li data-section-id="8ajv2n" data-start="1297" data-end="1323">
<p data-start="1299" data-end="1323">What each column means</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ec3yqg" data-start="1324" data-end="1359">
<p data-start="1326" data-end="1359">Data types (date, number, text)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pjx71e" data-start="1360" data-end="1382">
<p data-start="1362" data-end="1382">Any missing values</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1384" data-end="1421">👉 This step = <strong data-start="1399" data-end="1421">Data Understanding</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1423" data-end="1426">
<h2 data-section-id="14j4dvf" data-start="1428" data-end="1474">🧹 STEP 2: Data Cleaning (Create NEW SHEET)</h2>
<p data-start="1476" data-end="1513">👉 Create new sheet: <strong data-start="1497" data-end="1513">“Clean_Data”</strong></p>
<p data-start="1515" data-end="1523">Do this:</p>
<ul data-start="1525" data-end="1682">
<li data-section-id="1o1s9ka" data-start="1525" data-end="1546">
<p data-start="1527" data-end="1546">Remove duplicates</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="61gm0y" data-start="1547" data-end="1580">
<p data-start="1549" data-end="1580">Check blanks (fill or remove)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ig5uyv" data-start="1581" data-end="1638">
<p data-start="1583" data-end="1590">Format:</p>
<ul data-start="1593" data-end="1638">
<li data-section-id="1vk1rbb" data-start="1593" data-end="1617">
<p data-start="1595" data-end="1617">Date → proper format</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wep5kh" data-start="1620" data-end="1638">
<p data-start="1622" data-end="1638">Sales → number</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="144tv30" data-start="1639" data-end="1682">
<p data-start="1641" data-end="1682">Standardize text (no spelling variations)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1684" data-end="1719">👉 This step = <strong data-start="1699" data-end="1719">Data Preparation</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1721" data-end="1724">
<h2 data-section-id="odwpn5" data-start="1726" data-end="1774">🧠 STEP 3: Data Enhancement (Add New Columns)</h2>
<p data-start="1776" data-end="1814">👉 Now think like analyst, not student</p>
<p data-start="1816" data-end="1820">Add:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="o94hen" data-start="1822" data-end="1841">1. Month Column</h3>
<p data-start="1842" data-end="1894">Extract from Order Date<br data-start="1865" data-end="1868">
👉 Helps in trend analysis</p>
<hr data-start="1896" data-end="1899">
<h3 data-section-id="4i71xs" data-start="1901" data-end="1924">2. Revenue Category</h3>
<p data-start="1925" data-end="1940">Use IF formula:</p>
<ul data-start="1942" data-end="1991">
<li data-section-id="v4rx93" data-start="1942" data-end="1957">
<p data-start="1944" data-end="1957">High (&gt;50k)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15yfghs" data-start="1958" data-end="1978">
<p data-start="1960" data-end="1978">Medium (20k–50k)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="jobrk8" data-start="1979" data-end="1991">
<p data-start="1981" data-end="1991">Low (&lt;20k)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1993" data-end="1996">
<h3 data-section-id="dxf8v4" data-start="1998" data-end="2023">3. Order Count Column</h3>
<p data-start="2024" data-end="2085">Put “1” in all rows<br data-start="2043" data-end="2046">
👉 Helps in counting orders using pivot</p>
<hr data-start="2087" data-end="2090">
<p data-start="2092" data-end="2147">👉 This step = <strong data-start="2107" data-end="2147">Feature Engineering (important word)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2149" data-end="2152">
<h2 data-section-id="1vmbfjy" data-start="2154" data-end="2197">📊 STEP 4: KPI Creation (Separate Sheet)</h2>
<p data-start="2199" data-end="2233">👉 Create sheet: <strong data-start="2216" data-end="2233">“KPI_Summary”</strong></p>
<p data-start="2235" data-end="2245">Calculate:</p>
<ul data-start="2247" data-end="2363">
<li data-section-id="lkiyma" data-start="2247" data-end="2262">
<p data-start="2249" data-end="2262">Total Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11j7l93" data-start="2263" data-end="2279">
<p data-start="2265" data-end="2279">Total Orders</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="gm8tv2" data-start="2280" data-end="2303">
<p data-start="2282" data-end="2303">Average Order Value</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9o1oaj" data-start="2304" data-end="2318">
<p data-start="2306" data-end="2318">Top Region</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i30g08" data-start="2319" data-end="2334">
<p data-start="2321" data-end="2334">Top Product</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="bl85k2" data-start="2335" data-end="2363">
<p data-start="2337" data-end="2363">% Sales by Customer Type</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2365" data-end="2405">👉 These are <strong data-start="2378" data-end="2405">decision-making numbers</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2407" data-end="2410">
<h2 data-section-id="11ldoxh" data-start="2412" data-end="2454">🔁 STEP 5: Pivot Tables (Core Analysis)</h2>
<p data-start="2456" data-end="2487">👉 Create sheet: <strong data-start="2473" data-end="2487">“Analysis”</strong></p>
<p data-start="2489" data-end="2495">Build:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1ae34k2" data-start="2497" data-end="2521">1. Sales by Region</h3>
<h3 data-section-id="1y4rb5u" data-start="2522" data-end="2547">2. Sales by Product</h3>
<h3 data-section-id="kp797c" data-start="2548" data-end="2574">3. Sales by Category</h3>
<h3 data-section-id="rmtuzb" data-start="2575" data-end="2606">4. Sales by Month (Trend)</h3>
<h3 data-section-id="19mxlg2" data-start="2607" data-end="2638">5. Sales by Customer Type</h3>
<p data-start="2640" data-end="2672">👉 This step = <strong data-start="2655" data-end="2672">Data Analysis</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2674" data-end="2677">
<h2 data-section-id="y4dqox" data-start="2679" data-end="2725">📈 STEP 6: Dashboard Creation (Final Sheet)</h2>
<p data-start="2727" data-end="2759">👉 Create sheet: <strong data-start="2744" data-end="2759">“Dashboard”</strong></p>
<p data-start="2761" data-end="2781">Structure like this:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="whuahq" data-start="2783" data-end="2802">🔝 Top Section:</h3>
<ul data-start="2803" data-end="2828">
<li data-section-id="wizlls" data-start="2803" data-end="2828">
<p data-start="2805" data-end="2828">KPI Cards (big numbers)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="i7pzae" data-start="2830" data-end="2844">📊 Middle:</h3>
<ul data-start="2845" data-end="2907">
<li data-section-id="1nqsnlr" data-start="2845" data-end="2876">
<p data-start="2847" data-end="2876">Sales by Region (bar chart)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pjfy3l" data-start="2877" data-end="2907">
<p data-start="2879" data-end="2907">Sales by Product (pie chart)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="6zb4h3" data-start="2909" data-end="2923">📉 Bottom:</h3>
<ul data-start="2924" data-end="2952">
<li data-section-id="1qank87" data-start="2924" data-end="2952">
<p data-start="2926" data-end="2952">Monthly trend (line chart)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="d2ks6n" data-start="2954" data-end="2967">🎛️ Side:</h3>
<ul data-start="2968" data-end="3025">
<li data-section-id="liet0r" data-start="2968" data-end="3025">
<p data-start="2970" data-end="2978">Slicers:</p>
<ul data-start="2981" data-end="3025">
<li data-section-id="nj2lcg" data-start="2981" data-end="2991">
<p data-start="2983" data-end="2991">Region</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gybhab" data-start="2994" data-end="3005">
<p data-start="2996" data-end="3005">Product</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14zg09g" data-start="3008" data-end="3025">
<p data-start="3010" data-end="3025">Customer Type</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3027" data-end="3030">
<h2 data-section-id="1bebjcq" data-start="3032" data-end="3066">🎨 STEP 7: Make it PROFESSIONAL</h2>
<ul data-start="3068" data-end="3147">
<li data-section-id="t1qm2x" data-start="3068" data-end="3081">
<p data-start="3070" data-end="3081">Add title</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="o9kre" data-start="3082" data-end="3100">
<p data-start="3084" data-end="3100">Align properly</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qf45d1" data-start="3101" data-end="3126">
<p data-start="3103" data-end="3126">Use consistent colors</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xj1uaz" data-start="3127" data-end="3147">
<p data-start="3129" data-end="3147">Remove gridlines</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3149" data-end="3187">👉 This step = <strong data-start="3164" data-end="3187">Presentation Skills</strong></p>
<hr data-start="3189" data-end="3192">
<h2 data-section-id="904w58" data-start="3194" data-end="3233">🧠 STEP 8: INSIGHTS (MOST IMPORTANT)</h2>
<p data-start="3235" data-end="3264">👉 Create small text section:</p>
<p data-start="3266" data-end="3286">Write insights like:</p>
<ul data-start="3288" data-end="3424">
<li data-section-id="1q7zo6w" data-start="3288" data-end="3331">
<p data-start="3290" data-end="3331">“West region contributes highest sales”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1blcwmo" data-start="3332" data-end="3376">
