</li>
<li data-section-id="rg8efk" data-start="3377" data-end="3424">
<p data-start="3379" data-end="3424">“Returning customers generate more revenue”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3426" data-end="3470">👉 THIS is what makes your project strong 💥</p>
