<hr data-start="361" data-end="364">
<h2 data-section-id="1a037u3" data-start="366" data-end="401">🔥 Truth about “Strong Projects”</h2>
<p data-start="403" data-end="438">A project is not strong because of:</p>
<ul data-start="439" data-end="478">
<li data-section-id="1rznzk7" data-start="439" data-end="455">
