<h2 data-section-id="1uhuq68" data-start="586" data-end="645">🧠 Let me UPGRADE your project (Now it becomes powerful)</h2>
<p data-start="647" data-end="676">We’ll turn your project from:</p>
<p data-start="678" data-end="732">🟡 “Dashboard maker”<br data-start="698" data-end="701">
➡️ into<br data-start="708" data-end="711">
🟢 “Business analyst”</p>
<hr data-start="734" data-end="737">
<h1 data-section-id="1vh3ixj" data-start="739" data-end="791">🚀 ADVANCED VERSION (This is what makes it strong)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1lhxy18" data-start="793" data-end="821">🎯 Add BUSINESS QUESTIONS</h2>
<p data-start="823" data-end="854">Instead of just charts, answer:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1g0d304" data-start="856" data-end="883">1. Regional Performance</h3>
<p data-start="884" data-end="963">👉 Which region contributes most revenue?<br data-start="925" data-end="928">
👉 Which region is underperforming?</p>
<hr data-start="965" data-end="968">
<h3 data-section-id="1v8ehgj" data-start="970" data-end="993">2. Product Analysis</h3>
<p data-start="994" data-end="1089">👉 Which product gives high sales but low quantity?<br data-start="1045" data-end="1048">
👉 Which product should company focus on?</p>
<hr data-start="1091" data-end="1094">
<h3 data-section-id="l9og7n" data-start="1096" data-end="1120">3. Customer Behavior</h3>
<p data-start="1121" data-end="1202">👉 Are returning customers more valuable?<br data-start="1162" data-end="1165">
👉 Which type generates more revenue?</p>
<hr data-start="1204" data-end="1207">
<h3 data-section-id="1hrmc5c" data-start="1209" data-end="1226">4. Time Trend</h3>
<p data-start="1227" data-end="1300">👉 Which month had highest sales?<br data-start="1260" data-end="1263">
👉 Is sales increasing or decreasing?</p>
<hr data-start="1302" data-end="1305">
<h2 data-section-id="1lzb9vn" data-start="1307" data-end="1330">🔥 Add ADVANCED KPIs</h2>
<p data-start="1332" data-end="1352">Not basic ones. Add:</p>
<ul data-start="1354" data-end="1434">
<li data-section-id="lp3xkr" data-start="1354" data-end="1375">
<p data-start="1356" data-end="1375">Revenue per Order</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="isoyvr" data-start="1376" data-end="1408">
<p data-start="1378" data-end="1408">Contribution % (Region-wise)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kdr6fc" data-start="1409" data-end="1434">
<p data-start="1411" data-end="1434">Growth % (Month-wise)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1436" data-end="1474">👉 Now you’re thinking like analyst 💼</p>
<hr data-start="1476" data-end="1479">
<h2 data-section-id="1j6k8df" data-start="1481" data-end="1514">⚙️ Add Slightly Advanced Excel</h2>
<p data-start="1516" data-end="1520">Use:</p>
<ul data-start="1521" data-end="1630">
<li data-section-id="11nhcw9" data-start="1521" data-end="1553">
<p data-start="1523" data-end="1553"><strong data-start="1523" data-end="1533">SUMIFS</strong> (multi-condition)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14uwe23" data-start="1554" data-end="1573">
<p data-start="1556" data-end="1573"><strong data-start="1556" data-end="1571">IF (nested)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="otbg61" data-start="1574" data-end="1602">
<p data-start="1576" data-end="1602"><strong data-start="1576" data-end="1600">Pivot + Slicer combo</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16dx0rg" data-start="1603" data-end="1630">
<p data-start="1605" data-end="1630">Optional: <strong data-start="1615" data-end="1630">INDEX-MATCH</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
