<hr data-start="1098" data-end="1101">
<h2 data-section-id="jj3vl6" data-start="1103" data-end="1124">🎮 Think Like This</h2>
<p data-start="1126" data-end="1164">Two people cook with same ingredients:</p>
<ul data-start="1166" data-end="1233">
<li data-section-id="obcev7" data-start="1166" data-end="1193">
<p data-start="1168" data-end="1193">One makes plain food 🍚</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1h2u0j" data-start="1194" data-end="1233">
<p data-start="1196" data-end="1233">One makes restaurant-level dish 🍽️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1235" data-end="1277">👉 Ingredients same<br data-start="1254" data-end="1257">
👉 Skill different</p>
<hr data-start="1279" data-end="1282">
<h2 data-section-id="7cwyd0" data-start="1284" data-end="1301">⚡ Final Answer</h2>
<p data-start="1303" data-end="1365">👉 ❌ Not just language change<br data-start="1332" data-end="1335">
👉 ✅ Whole <strong data-start="1346" data-end="1365">mindset upgrade</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1367" data-end="1370">
<h2 data-section-id="wqqusl" data-start="1372" data-end="1400">🚀 What YOU should do now</h2>
<p data-start="1402" data-end="1487">Follow:<br>
👉 Structure (from first explanation)<br data-start="1447" data-end="1450">
👉 Thinking (from second explanation)</p>
<hr data-start="1489" data-end="1492">
<p data-start="1494" data-end="1515">If you’re ready, say:</p>
<p data-start="1517" data-end="1544"><strong data-start="1517" data-end="1544">“Start Step 2 advanced”</strong></p>
<p data-start="1546" data-end="1589" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Now we’ll build this like a real analyst 🔥</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#2126ae" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Share" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#630ca2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary touch:w-10 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" aria-label="More actions" type="button" id="radix-_r_160_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#f6d0e2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-(--header-height)" dir="auto" data-turn-id="f49b2e7c-8e17-4f5b-913a-65b13eaf9aea" data-testid="conversation-turn-41" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)" style="scroll-margin-top: -40px;"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="f49b2e7c-8e17-4f5b-913a-65b13eaf9aea" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">but i dont know how to anyxze pattenr what is bsuiness uwdtion what insight should i right</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-WEB:7db6c802-7c43-47fb-9316-1a3dfc040aaa-43" data-testid="conversation-turn-42" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant" style=""><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="a5b9d87e-c019-43e5-b12f-7ab5d61b18ab" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="30">First, your corrected version:</p>
<p data-start="32" data-end="142"><strong data-start="32" data-end="142">“But I don’t know how to analyze patterns. What are business questions, and what insights should I write?”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="144" data-end="147">
<p data-start="149" data-end="253">Good. This is the <strong data-start="167" data-end="189">real turning point</strong> 🧠⚡<br data-start="193" data-end="196">
This is exactly where beginners stop… and analysts start.</p>
<p data-start="255" data-end="307">Let’s break it so simply that it <em data-start="288" data-end="304">clicks forever</em> 👇</p>
<hr data-start="309" data-end="312">
<h1 data-section-id="t5yger" data-start="314" data-end="351">🧠 1. What is “Analyzing Patterns”?</h1>
<p data-start="353" data-end="370">👉 It just means:</p>
<p data-start="372" data-end="450"><strong data-start="372" data-end="450">Looking at data and noticing what is happening repeatedly or significantly</strong></p>
<hr data-start="452" data-end="455">
<h3 data-section-id="pdnm7m" data-start="457" data-end="471">💡 Example</h3>
<p data-start="473" data-end="484">If you see:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="486" data-end="566" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="486" data-end="504"><tr data-start="486" data-end="504"><th data-start="486" data-end="495" data-col-size="sm" class="">Region</th><th data-start="495" data-end="504" data-col-size="sm" class="">Sales</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="523" data-end="566"><tr data-start="523" data-end="544"><td data-start="523" data-end="532" data-col-size="sm">West</td><td data-start="532" data-end="544" data-col-size="sm">3,00,000</td></tr><tr data-start="545" data-end="566"><td data-start="545" data-end="554" data-col-size="sm">East</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="554" data-end="566">1,20,000</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="568" data-end="608">👉 Pattern = West is consistently higher</p>
<p data-start="610" data-end="701">👉 Insight =<br data-start="622" data-end="625">
<strong data-start="625" data-end="701">“West region is the top-performing region contributing highest revenue.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="703" data-end="706">
<h1 data-section-id="18r1bww" data-start="708" data-end="746">🎯 2. What are “Business Questions”?</h1>
<p data-start="748" data-end="788">These are questions a manager would ask.</p>
<p data-start="790" data-end="838">👉 Not Excel questions<br data-start="812" data-end="815">
👉 Real-world questions</p>
<hr data-start="840" data-end="843">
<h3 data-section-id="1xf7pqe" data-start="845" data-end="861">💼 Examples:</h3>
<ul data-start="863" data-end="1010">
<li data-section-id="zohws1" data-start="863" data-end="897">
<p data-start="865" data-end="897">Which region gives most sales?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3c2lm5" data-start="898" data-end="932">
<p data-start="900" data-end="932">Which product is best selling?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xb7ozh" data-start="933" data-end="974">
<p data-start="935" data-end="974">Which customer type is more valuable?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="eupzv7" data-start="975" data-end="1010">
<p data-start="977" data-end="1010">Are sales increasing over time?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1012" data-end="1047">👉 Your dashboard must answer these</p>
<hr data-start="1049" data-end="1052">
<h1 data-section-id="eje3fo" data-start="1054" data-end="1083">🔥 3. What is an “Insight”?</h1>
<p data-start="1085" data-end="1122">👉 Insight = <strong data-start="1098" data-end="1122">Conclusion from data</strong></p>
<p data-start="1124" data-end="1173">Not data<br data-start="1132" data-end="1135">
Not chart<br data-start="1144" data-end="1147">
👉 <strong data-start="1150" data-end="1173">Meaning of the data</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1175" data-end="1178">
<h2 data-section-id="ztievs" data-start="1180" data-end="1204">❌ Wrong (Not Insight)</h2>
<p data-start="1205" data-end="1228">“West sales = 3,00,000”</p>
<h2 data-section-id="1fd1ks9" data-start="1230" data-end="1252">✅ Correct (Insight)</h2>
<p data-start="1253" data-end="1304">“West region is the highest contributor to revenue”</p>
<hr data-start="1306" data-end="1309">
<h1 data-section-id="1b1z9on" data-start="1311" data-end="1354">🧠 SIMPLE FORMULA (Remember this forever)</h1>
<p data-start="1356" data-end="1387">👉 <strong data-start="1359" data-end="1387">Data → Pattern → Insight</strong></p>
<p data-start="1389" data-end="1397">Example:</p>
<ul data-start="1399" data-end="1501">
<li data-section-id="yasdda" data-start="1399" data-end="1424">
<p data-start="1401" data-end="1424">Data → West = highest</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="aof0fj" data-start="1425" data-end="1457">
<p data-start="1427" data-end="1457">Pattern → West always higher</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qsrsu4" data-start="1458" data-end="1501">
<p data-start="1460" data-end="1501">Insight → West is top-performing region</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1503" data-end="1506">
<h1 data-section-id="1w9fv60" data-start="1508" data-end="1555">🎯 4. What YOU should analyze in your project</h1>
<p data-start="1557" data-end="1578">Use this checklist 👇</p>
<hr data-start="1580" data-end="1583">
<h2 data-section-id="qethk7" data-start="1585" data-end="1609">📊 1. Region Analysis</h2>
<p data-start="1610" data-end="1614">Ask:</p>
<ul data-start="1615" data-end="1670">
<li data-section-id="4vx770" data-start="1615" data-end="1650">
<p data-start="1617" data-end="1650">Which region has highest sales?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gokvae" data-start="1651" data-end="1670">
<p data-start="1653" data-end="1670">Which has lowest?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1672" data-end="1746">👉 Insight example:<br data-start="1691" data-end="1694">
“North region is underperforming compared to others”</p>
<hr data-start="1748" data-end="1751">
<h2 data-section-id="14i6rtn" data-start="1753" data-end="1778">📦 2. Product Analysis</h2>
<p data-start="1779" data-end="1783">Ask:</p>
<ul data-start="1784" data-end="1844">
<li data-section-id="1ovrvmp" data-start="1784" data-end="1813">
<p data-start="1786" data-end="1813">Which product sells most?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1brw86q" data-start="1814" data-end="1844">
<p data-start="1816" data-end="1844">Which gives highest revenue?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1846" data-end="1913">👉 Insight:<br data-start="1857" data-end="1860">
“Laptops generate highest revenue among all products”</p>
<hr data-start="1915" data-end="1918">
<h2 data-section-id="1y5bmf0" data-start="1920" data-end="1942">👥 3. Customer Type</h2>
<p data-start="1943" data-end="1947">Ask:</p>
<ul data-start="1948" data-end="1983">
<li data-section-id="k0pxla" data-start="1948" data-end="1983">
<p data-start="1950" data-end="1983">New vs Returning → who buys more?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1985" data-end="2051">👉 Insight:<br data-start="1996" data-end="1999">
“Returning customers contribute majority of revenue”</p>
<hr data-start="2053" data-end="2056">
<h2 data-section-id="1io9qlc" data-start="2058" data-end="2080">📅 4. Time Analysis</h2>
<p data-start="2081" data-end="2085">Ask:</p>
<ul data-start="2086" data-end="2118">
<li data-section-id="1812xqc" data-start="2086" data-end="2118">
<p data-start="2088" data-end="2118">Which month has highest sales?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2120" data-end="2184">👉 Insight:<br data-start="2131" data-end="2134">
“Sales peaked in March indicating seasonal demand”</p>
<hr data-start="2186" data-end="2189">
<h1 data-section-id="1wn3kgw" data-start="2191" data-end="2237">⚡ 5. HOW to write insights (simple template)</h1>
<p data-start="2239" data-end="2248">Use this:</p>
<p data-start="2250" data-end="2300">👉 <strong data-start="2253" data-end="2300">[Thing] + is highest/lowest + reason/impact</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2302" data-end="2305">
<h3 data-section-id="1krudj" data-start="2307" data-end="2320">Examples:</h3>
<ul data-start="2322" data-end="2520">
<li data-section-id="15dgynb" data-start="2322" data-end="2384">
<p data-start="2324" data-end="2384">“West region contributes the highest share of total sales”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sf2who" data-start="2385" data-end="2453">
<p data-start="2387" data-end="2453">“Mobile category shows strong demand with highest quantity sold”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="z4ioi0" data-start="2454" data-end="2520">
<p data-start="2456" data-end="2520">“Returning customers generate more revenue than new customers”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2522" data-end="2525">
<h1 data-section-id="1bf85z6" data-start="2527" data-end="2560">🔥 Final Truth (Very Important)</h1>
<p data-start="2562" data-end="2650">👉 You don’t need “advanced brain”<br data-start="2596" data-end="2599">
👉 You just need to <strong data-start="2619" data-end="2650">observe and explain clearly</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2652" data-end="2655">
<h1 data-section-id="9f25ip" data-start="2657" data-end="2675">🚀 Your Task Now</h1>
<p data-start="2677" data-end="2697">When you open Excel:</p>
<p data-start="2699" data-end="2769">👉 Just ask:<br>
<strong data-start="2712" data-end="2769">“What is highest? What is lowest? What is different?”</strong></p>
<p data-start="2771" data-end="2787">That’s analysis.</p>
<hr data-start="2789" data-end="2792">
<p data-start="2794" data-end="2899">If you want next, I can:<br>
✅ Sit with you and say<br data-start="2841" data-end="2844">
👉 “Click this → now see this → now write this insight”</p>
<p data-start="2901" data-end="2910">Just say:</p>
<p data-start="2912" data-end="2941" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node=""><strong data-start="2912" data-end="2938">“Guide me while doing”</strong> 🔥</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-seconda