<p data-start="32" data-end="325"><strong data-start="32" data-end="325">“Now listen, let me tell you what I know in Excel. I want to include as much as possible in this project so that I can show I know everything. I don’t care if it becomes long or very big. I want that if a recruiter sees my project, they should feel I know everything and cannot reject me.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="327" data-end="330">
<h2 data-section-id="iha6xc" data-start="332" data-end="375">⚠️ Reality Check (important, don’t skip)</h2>
<p data-start="377" data-end="436">That idea sounds powerful… but it’s actually <strong data-start="422" data-end="435">dangerous</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="438" data-end="473">👉 If you try to “show everything”:</p>
<ul data-start="474" data-end="546">
<li data-section-id="d3t4s" data-start="474" data-end="499">
<p data-start="476" data-end="499">Project becomes messy</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nz9vw3" data-start="500" data-end="518">
<p data-start="502" data-end="518">No clear story</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fjezqv" data-start="519" data-end="546">
<p data-start="521" data-end="546">Recruiter gets confused</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="548" data-end="587">👉 And confused recruiter = ❌ rejection</p>
<hr data-start="589" data-end="592">
<h2 data-section-id="k3945o" data-start="594" data-end="629">🧠 What recruiters ACTUALLY want</h2>
<p data-start="631" data-end="635">Not:</p>
<blockquote data-start="636" data-end="660">
<p data-start="638" data-end="660">“She knows everything”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="662" data-end="666">But:</p>
<blockquote data-start="667" data-end="719">
<p data-start="669" data-end="719">“She knows the RIGHT things and applies them well”</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="721" data-end="724">
<h2 data-section-id="koygpj" data-start="726" data-end="776">🎯 BEST STRATEGY (This will make you stand out)</h2>
<p data-start="778" data-end="850">👉 Instead of “everything”<br data-start="804" data-end="807">
👉 Show <strong data-start="815" data-end="850">SMART + CLEAN + RELEVANT skills</strong></p>
<hr data-start="852" data-end="855">
<h1 data-section-id="x6oyc5" data-start="857" data-end="898">🔥 Your Project = “SMART POWER PROJECT”</h1>
<p data-start="900" data-end="916">We will include:</p>
<ul data-start="917" data-end="991">
<li data-section-id="1jnd9n" data-start="917" data-end="942">
<p data-start="919" data-end="942">Strong Excel skills ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="q3p9ej" data-start="943" data-end="966">
<p data-start="945" data-end="966">Business thinking ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8nt3j2" data-start="967" data-end="991">
<p data-start="969" data-end="991">Clean presentation ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="993" data-end="1030">👉 This = <strong data-start="1003" data-end="1030">unstoppable combination</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1032" data-end="1035">
<h2 data-section-id="u6wrl2" data-start="1037" data-end="1084">🧰 What we WILL include (carefully selected)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="db2hp2" data-start="1086" data-end="1105">✅ Data Cleaning</h3>
<ul data-start="1106" data-end="1167">
<li data-section-id="1o1s9ka" data-start="1106" data-end="1127">
<p data-start="1108" data-end="1127">Remove duplicates</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vvld17" data-start="1128" data-end="1145">
<p data-start="1130" data-end="1145">Handle blanks</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1i7xzh1" data-start="1146" data-end="1167">
<p data-start="1148" data-end="1167">Proper formatting</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1169" data-end="1172">
<h3 data-section-id="nygw1a" data-start="1174" data-end="1212">✅ Formulas (Important but limited)</h3>
<p data-start="1213" data-end="1217">Use:</p>
<ul data-start="1218" data-end="1294">
<li data-section-id="1363zbz" data-start="1218" data-end="1230">
<p data-start="1220" data-end="1230"><code data-start="1220" data-end="1228">SUMIFS</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3fzk2f" data-start="1231" data-end="1245">
<p data-start="1233" data-end="1245"><code data-start="1233" data-end="1243">COUNTIFS</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1avd3yj" data-start="1246" data-end="1263">
<p data-start="1248" data-end="1263"><code data-start="1248" data-end="1252">IF</code> (nested)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1moiq27" data-start="1264" data-end="1294">
<p data-start="1266" data-end="1294"><code data-start="1266" data-end="1275">XLOOKUP</code> or <code data-start="1279" data-end="1292">INDEX-MATCH</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1296" data-end="1333">👉 Enough to show skill, not overload</p>
<hr data-start="1335" data-end="1338">
<h3 data-section-id="f30whs" data-start="1340" data-end="1365">✅ Pivot Tables (CORE)</h3>
<ul data-start="1366" data-end="1424">
<li data-section-id="1nhekgz" data-start="1366" data-end="1385">
<p data-start="1368" data-end="1385">Sales by Region</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hw7nrk" data-start="1386" data-end="1406">
<p data-start="1388" data-end="1406">Sales by Product</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1s9rcec" data-start="1407" data-end="1424">
<p data-start="1409" data-end="1424">Monthly trend</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1426" data-end="1429">
<h3 data-section-id="199gylj" data-start="1431" data-end="1446">✅ Dashboard</h3>
<ul data-start="1447" data-end="1483">
