</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1607" data-end="1610">
<h3 data-section-id="ff34sd" data-start="1612" data-end="1651">✅ Insights Section (MOST IMPORTANT)</h3>
<p data-start="1652" data-end="1684">👉 This is where you beat others</p>
<hr data-start="1686" data-end="1689">
<h2 data-section-id="1igm175" data-start="1691" data-end="1715">❌ What we will NOT do</h2>
<ul data-start="1717" data-end="1813">
<li data-section-id="1yjafn2" data-start="1717" data-end="1757">
<p data-start="1719" data-end="1757">50 formulas just to show knowledge ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18yqbax" data-start="1758" data-end="1794">
<p data-start="1760" data-end="1794">Complex things without purpose ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9oju9z" data-start="1795" data-end="1813">
<p data-start="1797" data-end="1813">Messy design ❌</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1815" data-end="1818">
<h2 data-section-id="1ndxti6" data-start="1820" data-end="1837">🧠 Golden Rule</h2>
<p data-start="1839" data-end="1908">👉 “Don’t show everything you know”<br data-start="1874" data-end="1877">
👉 “Show you know what matters”</p>
<hr data-start="1910" data-end="1913">
<h2 data-section-id="jj3vl6" data-start="1915" data-end="1936">🎮 Think Like This</h2>
<p data-start="1938" data-end="2037">You’re not trying to impress with <strong data-start="1972" data-end="1982">volume</strong><br data-start="1982" data-end="1985">
👉 You’re impressing with <strong data-start="2011" data-end="2037">clarity + intelligence</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2039" data-end="2042">
<h2 data-section-id="1qyos99" data-start="2044" data-end="2076">💥 What recruiter should feel</h2>
<p data-start="2078" data-end="2082">Not:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2083" data-end="2103">
