</blockquote>
<p data-start="2105" data-end="2109">But:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2110" data-end="2176">
<p data-start="2112" data-end="2176">“This is clean, logical, and professional… she understands data”</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2178" data-end="2181">
<h2 data-section-id="5isx1q" data-start="2183" data-end="2222">⚡ Final Plan (Your Winning Strategy)</h2>
