<p data-start="32" data-end="689"><strong data-start="32" data-end="689">“Now listen, I know Power Query (joining two sheets, append, transformations), spin button with macro, pivot tables (multiple sheets, dynamic pivots), calculated fields, show values as, grouping, timeline, slicers, lookup formulas (VLOOKUP, XLOOKUP, INDEX-MATCH), dynamic lookups, text and date formulas, statistical and logical formulas, data validation, formatting, charts, dashboards, merging columns, conditional formatting, sorting, filtering, text to columns, and getting data into Power Query from different sources. I know I cannot include everything in one project, so based on these skills, give me a solid project that shows I know all this.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="691" data-end="694">
<p data-start="696" data-end="818">Now THIS is where things get serious 🔥<br data-start="735" data-end="738">
You actually have <strong data-start="756" data-end="771">good skills</strong>… now we package them into a <strong data-start="800" data-end="818">killer project</strong></p>
<hr data-start="820" data-end="823">
<h1 data-section-id="1ntqkrb" data-start="825" data-end="867">🎯 YOUR FINAL PROJECT (DESIGNED FOR YOU)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1kjjrxo" data-start="869" data-end="888">💼 Project Name:</h2>
<p data-start="889" data-end="970"><strong data-start="889" data-end="970">End-to-End Retail Sales Intelligence System (Excel + Power Query + Dashboard)</strong></p>
<p data-start="972" data-end="1008">👉 Sounds powerful? Good. It should.</p>
<hr data-start="1010" data-end="1013">
<h1 data-section-id="1x8qira" data-start="1015" data-end="1056">🧠 PROJECT STORY (This makes it strong)</h1>
<p data-start="1058" data-end="1095">You are working as a <strong data-start="1079" data-end="1095">Data Analyst</strong></p>
<p data-start="1097" data-end="1109">Company has:</p>
<ul data-start="1110" data-end="1176">
<li data-section-id="1yhkiwt" data-start="1110" data-end="1133">
<p data-start="1112" data-end="1133">Multiple data files</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="j4cp1o" data-start="1134" data-end="1153">
<p data-start="1136" data-end="1153">Messy structure</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1prpl6m" data-start="1154" data-end="1176">
<p data-start="1156" data-end="1176">No clear reporting</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1178" data-end="1224">👉 Your job:<br>
<strong data-start="1191" data-end="1224">Build a complete system that:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1225" data-end="1334">
<li data-section-id="1nh0j5f" data-start="1225" data-end="1255">
<p data-start="1227" data-end="1255">Imports data automatically</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i5l4rb" data-start="1256" data-end="1284">
<p data-start="1258" data-end="1284">Cleans and transforms it</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vmce3m" data-start="1285" data-end="1300">
<p data-start="1287" data-end="1300">Analyzes it</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wpdgmr" data-start="1301" data-end="1334">
<p data-start="1303" data-end="1334">Creates interactive dashboard</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1336" data-end="1339">
<h1 data-section-id="xhnxoy" data-start="1341" data-end="1375">🧭 PROJECT STRUCTURE (IMPORTANT)</h1>
<p data-start="1377" data-end="1404">You will NOT make one sheet</p>
<p data-start="1406" data-end="1434">You will create a <strong data-start="1424" data-end="1434">system</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1436" data-end="1439">
<h2 data-section-id="1aruzrd" data-start="1441" data-end="1469">📂 SHEET / FILE STRUCTURE</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="s4qzdq" data-start="1471" data-end="1504"><span role="text">1. <strong data-start="1478" data-end="1504">Raw_Data (Don’t touch)</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="1505" data-end="1524">👉 Original dataset</p>
<hr data-start="1526" data-end="1529">
<h3 data-section-id="1dnrgc2" data-start="1531" data-end="1573"><span role="text">2. <strong data-start="1538" data-end="1570">Power Query (Backend Engine)</strong> ⚙️</span></h3>
<p data-start="1574" data-end="1600">👉 THIS is where you shine</p>
<p data-start="1602" data-end="1611">You will:</p>
<ul data-start="1612" data-end="1729">
<li data-section-id="fddmyi" data-start="1612" data-end="1641">
<p data-start="1614" data-end="1641">Import data (Excel / CSV)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8s7vh" data-start="1642" data-end="1656">
<p data-start="1644" data-end="1656">Clean data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o74zs1" data-start="1657" data-end="1678">
<p data-start="1659" data-end="1678">Transform columns</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xt526b" data-start="1679" data-end="1704">
<p data-start="1681" data-end="1704">Append multiple files</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zk6e25" data-start="1705" data-end="1729">
<p data-start="1707" data-end="1729">Merge tables (joins)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1731" data-end="1770">💥 This alone makes your project strong</p>
<hr data-start="1772" data-end="1775">
<h3 data-section-id="2igxry" data-start="1777" data-end="1802"><span role="text">3. <strong data-start="1784" data-end="1802">Processed_Data</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="1803" data-end="1829">👉 Output from Power Query</p>
<hr data-start="1831" data-end="1834">
<h3 data-section-id="17awjp4" data-start="1836" data-end="1869"><span role="text">4. <strong data-start="1843" data-end="1869">Analysis (Pivot Layer)</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="1870" data-end="1905">👉 Pivot tables + calculated fields</p>
<hr data-start="1907" data-end="1910">
<h3 data-section-id="1yza16k" data-start="1912" data-end="1946"><span role="text">5. <strong data-start="1919" data-end="1943">Dashboard (Final UI)</strong> 🎨</span></h3>
<p data-start="1947" data-end="1969">👉 What recruiter sees</p>
<hr data-start="1971" data-end="1974">
<h1 data-section-id="11y5we0" data-start="1976" data-end="2012">🔥 WHAT YOU WILL INCLUDE (SMARTLY)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="16yiik1" data-start="2014" data-end="2048">⚙️ 1. Power Query (MAIN WEAPON)</h2>
<p data-start="2050" data-end="2054">Use:</p>
<ul data-start="2055" data-end="2144">
<li data-section-id="1rh6iw2" data-start="2055" data-end="2082">
<p data-start="2057" data-end="2082">Append (multiple files)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vp73a8" data-start="2083" data-end="2100">
<p data-start="2085" data-end="2100">Merge (joins)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bnd5kt" data-start="2101" data-end="2118">
<p data-start="2103" data-end="2118">Data cleaning</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ycg4b3" data-start="2119" data-end="2144">
<p data-start="2121" data-end="2144">Column transformation</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2146" data-end="2180">👉 This shows <strong data-start="2160" data-end="2180">real-world skill</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2182" data-end="2185">
<h2 data-section-id="b5nrob" data-start="2187" data-end="2218">📊 2. Pivot Table (ADVANCED)</h2>
