<hr data-start="116" data-end="119">
<h2 data-section-id="1s24mwt" data-start="121" data-end="188">😏 Good news… you’re actually OVERQUALIFIED for an Excel project</h2>
<p data-start="190" data-end="206">You’re thinking:</p>
<blockquote data-start="207" data-end="228">
<p data-start="209" data-end="228">“I only know Excel”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="230" data-end="307">But reality:<br>
👉 You know <strong data-start="255" data-end="307">advanced Excel + Power Query + automation basics</strong></p>
