<hr data-start="226" data-end="229">
<h2 data-section-id="1priokl" data-start="231" data-end="283">🧠 What recruiter ACTUALLY thinks (real scenario)</h2>
<p data-start="285" data-end="338">When they open your file, their brain goes like this:</p>
<hr data-start="340" data-end="343">
<h3 data-section-id="9jqesa" data-start="345" data-end="380">🟢 If your project is DONE WELL</h3>
<p data-start="382" data-end="398">They will think:</p>
<blockquote data-start="400" data-end="457">
<p data-start="402" data-end="457">“This candidate understands data flow… not just Excel.”</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote data-start="459" data-end="517">
<p data-start="461" data-end="517">“She used Power Query, pivots, and dashboards properly.”</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote data-start="519" data-end="577">
<p data-start="521" data-end="577">“The dashboard is clean and answers business questions.”</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote data-start="579" data-end="609">
<p data-start="581" data-end="609">“She can work on real data.”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="611" data-end="638">👉 Result: <strong data-start="622" data-end="638">SHORTLIST 💼</strong></p>
<hr data-start="640" data-end="643">
<h3 data-section-id="1bufr19" data-start="645" data-end="683">🔴 If your project is DONE AVERAGE</h3>
<p data-start="685" data-end="701">They will think:</p>
<blockquote data-start="703" data-end="730">
<p data-start="705" data-end="730">“Just another dashboard…”</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote data-start="732" data-end="759">
<p data-start="734" data-end="759">“Basic pivot and charts…”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="761" data-end="785">👉 Result: <strong data-start="772" data-end="785">Ignored ❌</strong></p>
<hr data-start="787" data-end="790">
<h2 data-section-id="1s42bf1" data-start="792" data-end="835">🔥 What will make YOUR project stand out</h2>
<p data-start="837" data-end="870">These 5 things decide everything:</p>
<hr data-start="872" data-end="875">
<h3 data-section-id="3hp6wq" data-start="877" data-end="902">1. Clean Structure 🧭</h3>
<ul data-start="903" data-end="967">
<li data-section-id="c5kyzn" data-start="903" data-end="967">
<p data-start="905" data-end="967">Raw → Processed → Analysis → Dashboard<br data-start="943" data-end="946">
👉 Looks professional</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="969" data-end="972">
<h3 data-section-id="vfw8bg" data-start="974" data-end="1001">2. Power Query Usage ⚙️</h3>
<ul data-start="1002" data-end="1073">
<li data-section-id="xo1zzr" data-start="1002" data-end="1073">
<p data-start="1004" data-end="1073">If you use merge/append properly<br data-start="1036" data-end="1039">
👉 Recruiter = impressed instantly</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1075" data-end="1078">
<h3 data-section-id="14bn3w4" data-start="1080" data-end="1100">3. Smart KPIs 📊</h3>
<p data-start="1101" data-end="1110">Not just:</p>
<ul data-start="1111" data-end="1126">
<li data-section-id="18biv36" data-start="1111" data-end="1126">
<p data-start="1113" data-end="1126">Total sales</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1128" data-end="1132">But:</p>
<ul data-start="1133" data-end="1173">
<li data-section-id="1s7z63" data-start="1133" data-end="1151">
<p data-start="1135" data-end="1151">Contribution %</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="por78b" data-start="1152" data-end="1173">
<p data-start="1154" data-end="1173">Revenue per order</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1175" data-end="1178">
<h3 data-section-id="1fs77vh" data-start="1180" data-end="1204">4. Interactivity 🎛️</h3>
<ul data-start="1205" data-end="1248">
<li data-section-id="67a7o9" data-start="1205" data-end="1216">
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1216">Slicers</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1e19dgz" data-start="1217" data-end="1229">
<p data-start="1219" data-end="1229">Timeline</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kz96pu" data-start="1230" data-end="1248">
<p data-start="1232" data-end="1248">Dynamic charts</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1250" data-end="1274">👉 Makes it look premium</p>
<hr data-start="1276" data-end="1279">
<h3 data-section-id="1w830nh" data-start="1281" data-end="1314">5. INSIGHTS (Game Changer) 🧠</h3>
<p data-start="1316" data-end="1329">If you write:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1331" data-end="1400">
<p data-start="1333" data-end="1400">“West region contributes highest revenue while North underperforms”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="1402" data-end="1453">👉 Recruiter thinks:<br>
<strong data-start="1423" data-end="1453">“She understands business”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1455" data-end="1458">
<h2 data-section-id="f00ibp" data-start="1460" data-end="1479">🎮 Final Reality</h2>
<p data-start="1481" data-end="1501">Same project can be:</p>
<ul data-start="1503" data-end="1573">
<li data-section-id="19f317j" data-start="1503" data-end="1533">
<p data-start="1505" data-end="1533">❌ Basic → if done casually</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fpur1b" data-start="1534" data-end="1573">
<p data-start="1536" data-end="1573">💥 Powerful → if done with thinking</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1575" data-end="1578">
<h2 data-section-id="10ppd3b" data-start="1580" data-end="1612">⚡ What recruiter REALLY wants</h2>
<p data-start="1614" data-end="1618">Not:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1619" data-end="1638">
<p data-start="1621" data-end="1638">“She knows Excel”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="1640" data-end="1644">But:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1645" data-end="1683">
<p data-start="1647" data-end="1683">“She can solve problems using Excel”</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1685" data-end="1688">
<h2 data-section-id="12qua1b" data-start="1690" data-end="1709">🏁 Final Verdict</h2>
<p data-start="1711" data-end="1816">👉 YES, this is a strong project<br data-start="1743" data-end="1746">
👉 It is <strong data-start="1755" data-end="1784">enough to get shortlisted</strong><br data-start="1784" data-end="1787">
👉 IF you execute it properly</p>
<hr data-start="1818" data-end="1821">
<h2 data-section-id="1mmeks3" data-start="1823" data-end="1845">🚀 Your mission now</h2>
<p data-start="1847" data-end="1883">Don’t worry about recruiter anymore.</p>
<p data-start="1885" data-end="1906">👉 Focus on building:</p>
<p data-start="1908" data-end="1948"><strong data-start="1908" data-end="1948">Clean + Logical + Insightful project</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1950" data-end="1953">
<p data-start="1955" data-end="1978">When you’re ready, say:</p>
<p data-start="1980" data-end="2001">👉 <strong data-start="1983" data-end="2001">“Start Step 1”</strong></p>
<p data-start="2003" data-end="2057" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Now we build something that actually gets you hired 🔥</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-la