 class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="0aede8ef-e5a7-4c04-a33c-d4f79bde4452" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="30">First, your corrected version:</p>
<p data-start="32" data-end="457"><strong data-start="32" data-end="457">“First, tell me the name of the project and what it means, because I am a fresher and only know advanced Excel. Then explain each step we will do, like raw data → cleaning → transformation → analysis → Power Query → pivot → KPI → insights. Also explain everything very simply, like to a 4-year-old, for example what revenue means and how we find it. Give me a full roadmap so I can follow it and build everything myself.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="459" data-end="462">
<p data-start="464" data-end="536">Alright. Now we build this <strong data-start="491" data-end="532">like a story, not like a boring class</strong> 🎮✨</p>
<hr data-start="538" data-end="541">
<h1 data-section-id="142vyhz" data-start="543" data-end="560">🎯 PROJECT NAME</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="16vbu7j" data-start="562" data-end="620"><span role="text">💼 <strong data-start="568" data-end="620">Retail Sales Dashboard &amp; Insights System (Excel)</strong></span></h2>
<hr data-start="622" data-end="625">
<h1 data-section-id="2x33fq" data-start="627" data-end="666">🧠 WHAT DOES THIS MEAN? (Very simple)</h1>
<p data-start="668" data-end="685">Imagine a shop 🏪</p>
<p data-start="687" data-end="697">Every day:</p>
<ul data-start="698" data-end="781">
<li data-section-id="6v7kt9" data-start="698" data-end="721">
<p data-start="700" data-end="721">People buy products</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="185h1mw" data-start="722" data-end="740">
<p data-start="724" data-end="740">Money comes in</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1woihl9" data-start="741" data-end="781">
<p data-start="743" data-end="781">Different cities perform differently</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="783" data-end="811">But the owner is confused 😵</p>
<p data-start="813" data-end="821">He says:</p>
<blockquote data-start="822" data-end="870">
<p data-start="824" data-end="870">“I have data… but I don’t understand anything”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="872" data-end="897">👉 YOU come in as analyst</p>
<p data-start="899" data-end="907">You say:</p>
<blockquote data-start="908" data-end="964">
<p data-start="910" data-end="964">“Don’t worry. I’ll turn your data into clear answers.”</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="966" data-end="969">
<h1 data-section-id="1tbmcj" data-start="971" data-end="984">🎯 YOUR JOB</h1>
<p data-start="986" data-end="1022">👉 Turn <strong data-start="994" data-end="1022">messy data → clear story</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1024" data-end="1027">
<h1 data-section-id="fnppos" data-start="1029" data-end="1061">🧭 FULL ROADMAP (SUPER SIMPLE)</h1>
<p data-start="1063" data-end="1111">We will go step-by-step like building a house 🏠</p>
<hr data-start="1113" data-end="1116">
<h2 data-section-id="56erzi" data-start="1118" data-end="1159">🥇 STEP 1: RAW DATA (Understand first)</h2>
<p data-start="1161" data-end="1188">👉 Open file<br data-start="1173" data-end="1176">
👉 Just LOOK</p>
<p data-start="1190" data-end="1194">Ask:</p>
<ul data-start="1195" data-end="1238">
<li data-section-id="1gixfo7" data-start="1195" data-end="1217">
<p data-start="1197" data-end="1217">What is this column?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="w3skyi" data-start="1218" data-end="1238">
<p data-start="1220" data-end="1238">What does it mean?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1240" data-end="1243">
<h3 data-section-id="1k6er7s" data-start="1245" data-end="1260">💡 Example:</h3>
<p data-start="1262" data-end="1289"><strong data-start="1262" data-end="1289">Sales = money earned 💰</strong></p>
<p data-start="1291" data-end="1294">If:</p>
<ul data-start="1295" data-end="1347">
<li data-section-id="jmha3f" data-start="1295" data-end="1347">
<p data-start="1297" data-end="1347">You sell laptop for ₹50,000<br data-start="1324" data-end="1327">
👉 Sales = ₹50,000</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1349" data-end="1352">
<p data-start="1354" data-end="1385">👉 That’s all. Don’t overthink.</p>
<hr data-start="1387" data-end="1390">
<h2 data-section-id="1nwhyrf" data-start="1392" data-end="1422">🥈 STEP 2: DATA CLEANING 🧹</h2>
<p data-start="1424" data-end="1457">👉 Make new sheet: <strong data-start="1443" data-end="1457">Clean_Data</strong></p>
<p data-start="1459" data-end="1479">Now clean like this:</p>
<ul data-start="1481" data-end="1542">
<li data-section-id="1o1s9ka" data-start="1481" data-end="1502">
<p data-start="1483" data-end="1502">Remove duplicates</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lx2nvk" data-start="1503" data-end="1522">
<p data-start="1505" data-end="1522">Fix blank cells</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ywn9kk" data-start="1523" data-end="1542">
<p data-start="1525" data-end="1542">Format properly</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1544" data-end="1547">
<h3 data-section-id="cfgzi9" data-start="1549" data-end="1560">🧠 Why?</h3>
<p data-start="1562" data-end="1625">Dirty data = wrong results ❌<br data-start="1590" data-end="1593">
Clean data = correct results ✅</p>
<hr data-start="1627" data-end="1630">
<h2 data-section-id="1kx0kwc" data-start="1632" data-end="1681">🥉 STEP 3: ADD NEW COLUMNS (Make data smarter)</h2>
<p data-start="1683" data-end="1710">Now we add brain to data 🧠</p>
<hr data-start="1712" data-end="1715">
<h3 data-section-id="1wchxuv" data-start="1717" data-end="1739">📅 1. Month Column</h3>
<p data-start="1741" data-end="1762">From date → get month</p>
<p data-start="1764" data-end="1802">Why?<br>
👉 To see <strong data-start="1779" data-end="1802">which month is best</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1804" data-end="1807">
<h3 data-section-id="kvmh7d" data-start="1809" data-end="1831">📦 2. Order Column</h3>
<p data-start="1833" data-end="1852">Put “1” in all rows</p>
<p data-start="1854" data-end="1889">Why?<br>
👉 To count total orders later</p>
<hr data-start="1891" data-end="1894">
<h3 data-section-id="1bon6iu" data-start="1896" data-end="1918">💡 Simple Example:</h3>
<p data-start="1920" data-end="1974">If 5 rows = 5 orders<br data-start="1940" data-end="1943">
👉 We sum column → total orders</p>
<hr data-start="1976" data-end="1979">
<h2 data-section-id="1krcrfd" data-start="1981" data-end="2030">🏅 STEP 4: POWER QUERY (Optional but powerful)</h2>
<p data-start="2032" data-end="2073">👉 Import data<br data-start="2046" data-end="2049">
👉 Clean automatically</p>
<p data-start="2075" data-end="2123">Think like:<br>
👉 “Machine is cleaning data for me”</p>
<hr data-start="2125" data-end="2128">
<h2 data-section-id="1uuvx5m" data-start="2130" data-end="2168">🏆 STEP 5: PIVOT TABLE (Magic step)</h2>
<p data-start="2170" data-end="2200">👉 This step answers questions</p>
<hr data-start="2202" data-end="2205">
<h3 data-section-id="2h9xop" data-start="2207" data-end="2231">🎯 Example Question:</h3>
<p data-start="2233" data-end="2269">👉 “Which region has highest sales?”</p>
<hr data-start="2271" data-end="2274">
<h3 data-section-id="cfgtbr" data-start="2276" data-end="2287">🧠 How?</h3>
<p data-start="2289" data-end="2303">We tell Excel:</p>
<ul data-start="2305" data-end="2347">
<li data-section-id="1188150" data-start="2305" data-end="2329">
<p data-start="2307" data-end="2329">Group data by Region</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n04lb4" data-start="2330" data-end="2347">
<p data-start="2332" data-end="2347">Add all sales</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2349" data-end="2352">
<h3 data-section-id="gk1xkv" data-start="2354" data-end="2368">💡 Output:</h3>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="2370" data-end="2450" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="2370" data-end="2388"><tr data-start="2370" data-end="2388"><th data-start="2370" data-end="2379" data-col-size="sm" class="">Region</th><th data-start="2379" data-end="2388" data-col-size="sm" class="">Sales</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="2407" data-end="2450"><tr data-start="2407" data-end="2428"><td data-start="2407" data-end="2416" data-col-size="sm">West</td><td data-start="2416" data-end="2428" data-col-size="sm">3,00,000</td></tr><tr data-start="2429" data-end="2450"><td data-start="2429" data-end="2438" data-col-size="sm">East</td><td data-start="2438" data-end="2450" data-col-size="sm">1,20,000</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="2452" data-end="2455">
<p data-start="2457" data-end="2478">👉 Now we SEE pattern</p>
<hr data-start="2480" data-end="2483">
<h2 data-section-id="1kxko99" data-start="2485" data-end="2516">🥇 STEP 6: KPI (Big numbers)</h2>
<p data-start="2518" data-end="2543">👉 KPI = important number</p>
<hr data-start="2545" data-end="2548">
<h3 data-section-id="1k6er7s" data-start="2550" data-end="2565">💡 Example:</h3>
<ul data-start="2567" data-end="2618">
<li data-section-id="g13xo7" data-start="2567" data-end="2595">
<p data-start="2569" data-end="2595">Total Sales = ₹10,00,000</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17il908" data-start="2596" data-end="2618">
<p data-start="2598" data-end="2618">Total Orders = 200</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2620" data-end="2623">
<p data-start="2625" data-end="2656">👉 These go on TOP of dashboard</p>
<hr data-start="2658" data-end="2661">
<h2 data-section-id="1wuxa5y" data-start="2663" data-end="2712">🧠 STEP 7: ANALYSIS (Think like detective 🕵️)</h2>
<p data-start="2714" data-end="2735">Ask simple questions:</p>
<hr data-start="2737" data-end="2740">
<h3 data-section-id="5jk4zp" data-start="2742" data-end="2776">📍 1. Which region is highest?</h3>
<p data-start="2778" data-end="2795">👉 Find MAX value</p>
<p data-start="2797" data-end="2819">👉 If West is highest:</p>
<p data-start="2821" data-end="2859">✅ Insight:<br>
“West region performs best”</p>
<hr data-start="2861" data-end="2864">
<h3 data-section-id="1r3gg7c" data-start="2866" data-end="2901">📦 2. Which product sells most?</h3>
<p data-start="2903" data-end="2925">👉 Check highest sales</p>
<hr data-start="2927" data-end="2930">
<h3 data-section-id="1rml65g" data-start="2932" data-end="2956">👥 3. Who buys more?</h3>
<p data-start="2958" data-end="2987">👉 New vs Returning customers</p>
<hr data-start="2989" data-end="2992">
<h2 data-section-id="1k12iab" data-start="2994" data-end="3032">📝 STEP 8: INSIGHTS (Write answers)</h2>
<p data-start="3034" data-end="3060">👉 Just write what you SEE</p>
<hr data-start="3062" data-end="3065">
<h3 data-section-id="a37b9h" data-start="3067" data-end="3085">❌ Don’t write:</h3>
<p data-start="3086" data-end="3101">“West = 300000”</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1q2j8lg" data-start="3103" data-end="3115">✅ Write:</h3>
<p data-start="3116" data-end="3147">“West region has highest sales”</p>
<hr data-start="3149" data-end="3152">
<p data-start="3154" data-end="3181">👉 Simple English is enough</p>
<hr data-start="3183" data-end="3186">
<h2 data-section-id="1pddr1q" data-start="3188" data-end="3224">🎨 STEP 9: DASHBOARD (Final look)</h2>
<p data-start="3226" data-end="3248">👉 Arrange everything:</p>
<ul data-start="3250" data-end="3302">
<li data-section-id="1ui9a9v" data-start="3250" data-end="3263">
<p data-start="3252" data-end="3263">Top → KPI</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="462nmw" data-start="3264" data-end="3283">
<p data-start="3266" data-end="3283">Middle → Charts</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6imr4i" data-start="3284" data-end="3302">
<p data-start="3286" data-end="3302">Side → Filters</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3304" data-end="3307">
<p data-start="3309" data-end="3349">👉 Make it clean (like neat notebook 📒)</p>
<hr data-start="3351" data-end="3354">
<h1 data-section-id="iimcf0" data-start="3356" data-end="3380">🎮 FINAL UNDERSTANDING</h1>
<p data-start="3382" data-end="3404">👉 You are doing this:</p>
<ul data-start="3406" data-end="3469">
<li data-section-id="d6ywuy" data-start="3406" data-end="3424">
<p data-start="3408" data-end="3424">Data → numbers</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1s1u28d" data-start="3425" data-end="3446">
<p data-start="3427" data-end="3446">Numbers → meaning</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5fzaod" data-start="3447" data-end="3469">
<p data-start="3449" data-end="3469">Meaning → decision</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3471" data-end="3474">
<h1 data-section-id="22tlzy" data-start="3476" data-end="3513">⚡ SIMPLE FORMULA (Remember forever)</h1>
<p data-start="3515" data-end="3554">👉 <strong data-start="3518" data-end="3554">Data → Pivot → Pattern → Insight</strong></p>
<hr data-start="3556" data-end="3559">
<h1 data-section-id="189h03z" data-start="3561" data-end="3581">🚀 WHAT YOU DO NOW</h1>
<p data-start="3583" data-end="3611">Don’t think about everything</p>
<p data-start="3613" data-end="3627">👉 Start ONLY:</p>
<h2 data-section-id="1jpkn95" data-start="3629" data-end="3650">👉 STEP 1 + STEP 2</h2>
<ul data-start="3652" data-end="3706">
<li data-section-id="1wrab0" data-start="3652" data-end="3665">
<p data-start="3654" data-end="3665">Open data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="86mne1" data-start="3666" data-end="3693">
<p data-start="3668" data-end="3693">Create Clean_Data sheet</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="u9hddc" data-start="3694" data-end="3706">
<p data-start="3696" data-end="3706">Clean it</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3708" data-end="3711">
<p data-start="3713" data-end="3728">When done, say:</p>
<p data-start="3730" data-end="3750">👉 <strong data-start="3733" data-end="3750">“Step 2 done”</strong></p>
<p data-start="3752" data-end="3795" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Then I’ll guide next step like a coach 🧠🔥</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad res