<p data-start="33" data-end="119"><strong data-start="33" data-end="119">“I have an Excel file, but when I open it, I cannot see the row and column lines.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="121" data-end="124">
<h2 data-section-id="4f1zz5" data-start="126" data-end="171">😄 Don’t worry — your Excel isn’t broken</h2>
<p data-start="172" data-end="206">It’s just <strong data-start="182" data-end="206">gridlines turned off</strong></p>
<p data-start="208" data-end="255">Think of it like your notebook without lines 📒</p>
<hr data-start="257" data-end="260">
<h2 data-section-id="1fgdh4b" data-start="262" data-end="291">✅ How to Fix (Very Simple)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="kr0plb" data-start="293" data-end="318">🔹 Method 1 (Fastest)</h3>
<ol data-start="320" data-end="396">
<li data-section-id="1y26xhv" data-start="320" data-end="343">
<p data-start="323" data-end="343">Go to <strong data-start="329" data-end="337">View</strong> tab</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="g8xfcw" data-start="344" data-end="371">
<p data-start="347" data-end="371">Look for <strong data-start="356" data-end="369">Gridlines</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ulp7rn" data-start="372" data-end="396">
<p data-start="375" data-end="396">✔ Tick the checkbox</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="398" data-end="428">👉 Lines will appear instantly</p>
<hr data-start="430" data-end="433">
<h3 data-section-id="j97joh" data-start="435" data-end="474">🔹 Method 2 (If above doesn’t work)</h3>
<ol data-start="476" data-end="569">
<li data-section-id="gdblef" data-start="476" data-end="506">
<p data-start="479" data-end="506">Go to <strong data-start="485" data-end="500">Page Layout</strong> tab</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lm4yrl" data-start="507" data-end="532">
<p data-start="510" data-end="532">In <strong data-start="513" data-end="530">Sheet Options</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wsdmaz" data-start="533" data-end="569">
<p data-start="536" data-end="569">Under Gridlines → ✔ Tick <strong data-start="561" data-end="569">View</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="571" data-end="574">
<h2 data-section-id="dwvrps" data-start="576" data-end="602">⚠️ If still not visible</h2>
<p data-start="604" data-end="615">Check this:</p>
<p data-start="617" data-end="657">👉 Cells might have <strong data-start="637" data-end="657">white fill color</strong></p>
<p data-start="659" data-end="663">Fix:</p>
<ol data-start="664" data-end="753">
<li data-section-id="ee0ina" data-start="664" data-end="702">
<p data-start="667" data-end="702">Select whole sheet (<strong data-start="687" data-end="699">Ctrl + A</strong>)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12n9dcc" data-start="703" data-end="731">
<p data-start="706" data-end="731">Go to <strong data-start="712" data-end="726">Fill Color</strong> 🎨</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1nj9b8r" data-start="732" data-end="753">
<p data-start="735" data-end="753">Choose <strong data-start="742" data-end="753">No Fill</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="755" data-end="758">
<h2 data-section-id="13f3d4j" data-start="760" data-end="778">🎯 Final Result</h2>
<p data-start="780" data-end="796">👉 You will see:</p>
<ul data-start="797" data-end="833">
<li data-section-id="6sc27l" data-start="797" data-end="805">
<p data-start="799" data-end="805">Rows</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="118qgvh" data-start="806" data-end="817">
<p data-start="808" data-end="817">Columns</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mep08q" data-start="818" data-end="833">
<p data-start="820" data-end="833">Proper grid</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="835" data-end="838">
<h2 data-section-id="uwourv" data-start="840" data-end="871">🚀 Now continue your project</h2>
<p data-start="873" data-end="897">Once gridlines are back:</p>
<p data-start="899" data-end="923">👉 Start cleaning data</p>
