" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-WEB:7db6c802-7c43-47fb-9316-1a3dfc040aaa-54" data-testid="conversation-turn-64" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant" style=""><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="cdfea667-52f7-4b1a-b458-7e85e1873140" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="31">First, your corrected sentence:</p>
<p data-start="33" data-end="76"><strong data-start="33" data-end="76">“When I press Ctrl + T, a sound comes.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="78" data-end="81">
<h2 data-section-id="12oxz0m" data-start="83" data-end="132">🔔 That “sound” = Excel saying ❌ “Not allowed”</h2>
<p data-start="134" data-end="214">Don’t worry. This happens for a few specific reasons. Let’s fix it like a pro 👇</p>
<hr data-start="216" data-end="219">
<h1 data-section-id="bb37d3" data-start="221" data-end="255">🔍 Most Likely Reasons (and FIX)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="ofu9q8" data-start="257" data-end="297">❌ 1. Sheet is Protected (Most common)</h2>
<p data-start="299" data-end="336">👉 Excel blocks actions → makes sound</p>
<h3 data-section-id="16dsxf2" data-start="338" data-end="348">✅ Fix:</h3>
<ol data-start="349" data-end="405">
<li data-section-id="1eggvd0" data-start="349" data-end="374">
<p data-start="352" data-end="374">Go to <strong data-start="358" data-end="368">Review</strong> tab</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o8z7ns" data-start="375" data-end="405">
<p data-start="378" data-end="405">Click <strong data-start="384" data-end="403">Unprotect Sheet</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="407" data-end="437">👉 Then try <strong data-start="419" data-end="431">Ctrl + T</strong> again</p>
<hr data-start="439" data-end="442">
<h2 data-section-id="151jk3d" data-start="444" data-end="475">❌ 2. You are not inside data</h2>
<p data-start="477" data-end="514">👉 Excel doesn’t know what to convert</p>
<h3 data-section-id="16dsxf2" data-start="516" data-end="526">✅ Fix:</h3>
<ol data-start="527" data-end="614">
<li data-section-id="183j4e1" data-start="527" data-end="563">
<p data-start="530" data-end="563">Click any cell inside your data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="l3d3vh" data-start="564" data-end="587">
<p data-start="567" data-end="587">Press <strong data-start="573" data-end="585">Ctrl + A</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="at8c72" data-start="588" data-end="614">
<p data-start="591" data-end="614">Then press <strong data-start="602" data-end="614">Ctrl + T</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="616" data-end="619">
<h2 data-section-id="m6fwq1" data-start="621" data-end="655">❌ 3. Merged Cells (VERY COMMON)</h2>
<p data-start="657" data-end="695">👉 Tables don’t work with merged cells</p>
<h3 data-section-id="16dsxf2" data-start="697" data-end="707">✅ Fix:</h3>
<ol data-start="708" data-end="795">
<li data-section-id="1hhelr2" data-start="708" data-end="731">
<p data-start="711" data-end="731">Press <strong data-start="717" data-end="729">Ctrl + A</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lqzshu" data-start="732" data-end="768">
<p data-start="735" data-end="768">Go to <strong data-start="741" data-end="766">Home → Merge &amp; Center</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ejudmo" data-start="769" data-end="795">
<p data-start="772" data-end="795">Click <strong data-start="778" data-end="795">Unmerge Cells</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="797" data-end="814">👉 Then try again</p>
<hr data-start="816" data-end="819">
<h2 data-section-id="6ng8f6" data-start="821" data-end="863">❌ 4. File is Read-Only / Protected Mode</h2>
<p data-start="865" data-end="906">👉 Downloaded files sometimes open locked</p>
<h3 data-section-id="16dsxf2" data-start="908" data-end="918">✅ Fix:</h3>
<p data-start="919" data-end="959">Look at top:<br>
👉 Click <strong data-start="941" data-end="959">Enable Editing</strong></p>
<hr data-start="961" data-end="964">
<h2 data-section-id="1jeo33q" data-start="966" data-end="999">❌ 5. You selected entire sheet</h2>
<p data-start="1001" data-end="1039">👉 Excel doesn’t like full sheet table</p>
<h3 data-section-id="16dsxf2" data-start="1041" data-end="1051">✅ Fix:</h3>
<p data-start="1052" data-end="1090">Select only data area, not whole sheet</p>
<hr data-start="1092" data-end="1095">
<h1 data-section-id="162bscr" data-start="1097" data-end="1135">🧠 Quick Checklist (Do this exactly)</h1>
<ol data-start="1137" data-end="1242">
<li data-section-id="ezbp6g" data-start="1137" data-end="1159">
<p data-start="1140" data-end="1159">Click inside data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="l3d3vh" data-start="1160" data-end="1183">
<p data-start="1163" data-end="1183">Press <strong data-start="1169" data-end="1181">Ctrl + A</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o5yka6" data-start="1184" data-end="1202">
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1202">Unmerge cells</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="yxtsma" data-start="1203" data-end="1222">
<p data-start="1206" data-end="1222">Enable editing</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="f0hs6v" data-start="1223" data-end="1242">
<p data-start="1226" data-end="1242">Try <strong data-start="1230" data-end="1242">Ctrl + T</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1244" data-end="1247">
<h2 data-section-id="8kz6s3" data-start="1249" data-end="1273">🎯 Still not working?</h2>
<p data-start="1275" data-end="1359">Tell me:<br>
👉 What type of file (.csv / .xlsx)?<br data-start="1320" data-end="1323">
👉 What happens exactly after sound?</p>
