<p data-start="33" data-end="112"><strong data-start="33" data-end="112">“What are the similar things between Excel and Power BI, like Power Query?”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="114" data-end="117">
<p data-start="119" data-end="251">Now let’s decode this properly 👇<br data-start="152" data-end="155">
Think of Excel and Power BI as <strong data-start="186" data-end="248">two cousins who share the same brain but dress differently</strong> 😄</p>
<hr data-start="253" data-end="256">
<h1 data-section-id="gk40ci" data-start="258" data-end="297">🧠 CORE SIMILARITIES (Most Important)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="17wkptg" data-start="299" data-end="336">⚙️ 1. Power Query (Same Engine 🔥)</h2>
<p data-start="338" data-end="414">👉 In Excel → “Get &amp; Transform Data”<br data-start="374" data-end="377">
👉 In Power BI → “Power Query Editor”</p>
<p data-start="416" data-end="425">Both can:</p>
<ul data-start="426" data-end="525">
<li data-section-id="8s7vh" data-start="426" data-end="440">
<p data-start="428" data-end="440">Clean data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o1s9ka" data-start="441" data-end="462">
<p data-start="443" data-end="462">Remove duplicates</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zk6e25" data-start="463" data-end="487">
<p data-start="465" data-end="487">Merge tables (joins)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="x8i7km" data-start="488" data-end="503">
<p data-start="490" data-end="503">Append data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o74zs1" data-start="504" data-end="525">
<p data-start="506" data-end="525">Transform columns</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="527" data-end="565">👉 Literally <strong data-start="540" data-end="565">same tool, same logic</strong></p>
<hr data-start="567" data-end="570">
<h2 data-section-id="1mq8oga" data-start="572" data-end="609">📊 2. Data Modeling (Concept same)</h2>
<p data-start="611" data-end="623">👉 Both can:</p>
<ul data-start="624" data-end="704">
<li data-section-id="1wt6np2" data-start="624" data-end="653">
<p data-start="626" data-end="653">Work with multiple tables</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cdachn" data-start="654" data-end="678">
<p data-start="656" data-end="678">Create relationships</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1erb8an" data-start="679" data-end="704">
<p data-start="681" data-end="704">Build structured data</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="706" data-end="720">⚠️ Difference:</p>
<ul data-start="721" data-end="795">
<li data-section-id="16vmr1m" data-start="721" data-end="760">
<p data-start="723" data-end="760">Excel → limited (needs Power Pivot)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1nj29a8" data-start="761" data-end="795">
<p data-start="763" data-end="795">Power BI → built-in &amp; stronger</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="797" data-end="800">
<h2 data-section-id="13bdqtp" data-start="802" data-end="826">🧮 3. Formulas vs DAX</h2>
<p data-start="828" data-end="837">👉 Excel:</p>
<ul data-start="838" data-end="862">
<li data-section-id="1o90do6" data-start="838" data-end="862">
<p data-start="840" data-end="862"><code data-start="840" data-end="845">SUM</code>, <code data-start="847" data-end="851">IF</code>, <code data-start="853" data-end="862">XLOOKUP</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="864" data-end="876">👉 Power BI:</p>
<ul data-start="877" data-end="909">
<li data-section-id="1e3nq2v" data-start="877" data-end="909">
<p data-start="879" data-end="909">DAX (<code data-start="884" data-end="889">SUM</code>, <code data-start="891" data-end="902">CALCULATE</code>, etc.)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="911" data-end="963">👉 Logic is SAME<br data-start="927" data-end="930">
👉 Syntax is slightly different</p>
<hr data-start="965" data-end="968">
<h2 data-section-id="19u9cqe" data-start="970" data-end="1010">📈 4. Pivot Table vs Power BI Visuals</h2>
<p data-start="1012" data-end="1021">👉 Excel:</p>
<ul data-start="1022" data-end="1037">
<li data-section-id="12tgc6a" data-start="1022" data-end="1037">
<p data-start="1024" data-end="1037">Pivot Table</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1039" data-end="1051">👉 Power BI:</p>
<ul data-start="1052" data-end="1078">
<li data-section-id="1f2m3f4" data-start="1052" data-end="1078">
<p data-start="1054" data-end="1078">Visuals (charts, tables)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1080" data-end="1088">👉 Both:</p>
<ul data-start="1089" data-end="1149">
<li data-section-id="1s3o4p3" data-start="1089" data-end="1103">
<p data-start="1091" data-end="1103">Group data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1e1mr33" data-start="1104" data-end="1128">
<p data-start="1106" data-end="1128">Aggregate (sum, avg)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kmiqlz" data-start="1129" data-end="1149">
<p data-start="1131" data-end="1149">Analyze patterns</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1151" data-end="1154">
<h2 data-section-id="1uqyrwb" data-start="1156" data-end="1183">🎛️ 5. Filters / Slicers</h2>
<p data-start="1185" data-end="1194">👉 Excel:</p>
<ul data-start="1195" data-end="1216">
<li data-section-id="perbv2" data-start="1195" data-end="1216">
<p data-start="1197" data-end="1216">Slicers, Timeline</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1218" data-end="1230">👉 Power BI:</p>
<ul data-start="1231" data-end="1251">
<li data-section-id="1f5hrty" data-start="1231" data-end="1251">
<p data-start="1233" data-end="1251">Filters, slicers</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1253" data-end="1300">👉 Same purpose:<br>
<strong data-start="1270" data-end="1300">Make dashboard interactive</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1302" data-end="1305">
<h2 data-section-id="uaui6r" data-start="1307" data-end="1333">🧠 6. KPIs &amp; Dashboards</h2>
<p data-start="1335" data-end="1347">👉 Both can:</p>
<ul data-start="1348" data-end="1405">
<li data-section-id="15u9e0x" data-start="1348" data-end="1368">
<p data-start="1350" data-end="1368">Show total sales</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hzpxf5" data-start="1369" data-end="1384">
<p data-start="1371" data-end="1384">Show trends</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1cox209" data-start="1385" data-end="1405">
<p data-start="1387" data-end="1405">Build dashboards</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1407" data-end="1448">👉 Goal is same:<br>
<strong data-start="1424" data-end="1448">Turn data → insights</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1450" data-end="1453">
<h1 data-section-id="eesd6q" data-start="1455" data-end="1477">🎯 SIMPLE COMPARISON</h1>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="1479" data-end="1641" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="1479" data-end="1499"><tr data-start="1479" data-end="1499"><th data-start="1479" data-end="1487" data-col-size="sm" class="">Excel</th><th data-start="1487" data-end="1499" data-col-size="sm" class="">Power BI</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="1519" data-end="1641"><tr data-start="1519" data-end="1548"><td data-start="1519" data-end="1533" data-col-size="sm">Power Query</td><td data-start="1533" data-end="1548" data-col-size="sm">Power Query</td></tr><tr data-start="1549" data-end="1574"><td data-start="1549" data-end="1563" data-col-size="sm">Pivot Table</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="1563" data-end="1574">Visuals</td></tr><tr data-start="1575" data-end="1593"><td data-start="1575" data-end="1586" data-col-size="sm">Formulas</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="1586" data-end="1593">DAX</td></tr><tr data-start="1594" data-end="1615"><td data-start="1594" data-end="1604" data-col-size="sm">Slicers</td><td data-start="1604" data-end="1615" data-col-size="sm">Filters</td></tr><tr data-start="1616" data-end="1641"><td data-start="1616" data-end="1628" data-col-size="sm">Dashboard</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="1628" data-end="1641">Dashboard</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="1643" data-end="1646">
<h1 data-section-id="1bhwttu" data-start="1648" data-end="1682">🔥 BIG TRUTH (Important for you)</h1>
<p data-start="1684" data-end="1742">👉 If you master Excel properly<br data-start="1715" data-end="1718">
👉 Power BI becomes EASY</p>
<p data-start="1744" data-end="1795">Because:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="1756" data-end="1795">Thinking is same, tool is different</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1797" data-end="1800">
<h1 data-section-id="1kdcrc9" data-start="1802" data-end="1822">🎮 Think Like This</h1>
<p data-start="1824" data-end="1903">Excel = 🛠️ Multi-purpose toolkit<br data-start="1857" data-end="1860">
Power BI = 🎯 Dedicated dashboard machine</p>
<hr data-start="1905" data-end="1908">
<h1 data-section-id="5kvf3r" data-start="1910" data-end="1926">⚡ Final Answer</h1>
<p data-start="1928" data-end="2021">👉 Yes, many things are similar<br data-start="1959" data-end="1962">
👉 Especially <strong data-start="1976" data-end="2021">Power Query, logic, and analysis thinking</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2023" data-end="2026">
<h2 data-section-id="1d0mtgg" data-start="2028" data-end="2041">🚀 For YOU</h2>
<p data-start="2043" data-end="2129">👉 What you’re learning in Excel project now<br data-start="2087" data-end="2090">
👉 Will directly help in Power BI later</p>
