<p data-start="33" data-end="169"><strong data-start="33" data-end="169">“How can I merge two columns where one has the initial of the name and the other has the last name, to get something like ‘H. Ram’?”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="171" data-end="174">
<h2 data-section-id="1aui9rn" data-start="176" data-end="186">🎯 Goal</h2>
<p data-start="187" data-end="196">You have:</p>
<ul data-start="197" data-end="270">
<li data-section-id="1fuu2wk" data-start="197" data-end="231">
<p data-start="199" data-end="231">Column A → Initial (e.g., <code data-start="225" data-end="228">H</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11xzm8i" data-start="232" data-end="270">
<p data-start="234" data-end="270">Column B → Last Name (e.g., <code data-start="262" data-end="267">Ram</code>)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="272" data-end="295">👉 You want: <strong data-start="285" data-end="295">H. Ram</strong></p>
<hr data-start="297" data-end="300">
<h2 data-section-id="1ww6dit" data-start="302" data-end="338">✅ Method 1: Simple Formula (Best)</h2>
<p data-start="340" data-end="357">Use this formula:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="359" data-end="382"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>=A2 &amp; ". " &amp; B2</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="384" data-end="387">
<h3 data-section-id="1y4yzex" data-start="389" data-end="423">🧠 How it works (super simple)</h3>
<ul data-start="425" data-end="496">
<li data-section-id="w7issh" data-start="425" data-end="437">
<p data-start="427" data-end="437"><code data-start="427" data-end="431">A2</code> → H</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="7ijfmh" data-start="438" data-end="458">
<p data-start="440" data-end="458"><code data-start="440" data-end="445">"."</code> → adds dot</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bwvurw" data-start="459" data-end="481">
<p data-start="461" data-end="481"><code data-start="461" data-end="466">" "</code> → adds space</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uxvs1g" data-start="482" data-end="496">
<p data-start="484" data-end="496"><code data-start="484" data-end="488">B2</code> → Ram</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="498" data-end="520">👉 Result = <strong data-start="510" data-end="520">H. Ram</strong></p>
<hr data-start="522" data-end="525">
<h2 data-section-id="gugo05" data-start="527" data-end="554">✅ Method 2: Using CONCAT</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="556" data-end="583"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>=CONCAT(A2,". ",B2)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="585" data-end="599">👉 Same result</p>
<hr data-start="601" data-end="604">
<h2 data-section-id="uxwbl" data-start="606" data-end="625">⚠️ Important Tip</h2>
<p data-start="627" data-end="660">If your initial is lowercase (h):</p>
<p data-start="662" data-end="674">👉 Use this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="676" data-end="706"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>=UPPER(A2) &amp; ". " &amp; B2</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="708" data-end="730">👉 Output = <strong data-start="720" data-end="730">H. Ram</strong></p>
<hr data-start="732" data-end="735">
<h2 data-section-id="7x4smk" data-start="737" data-end="762">💡 Bonus (Clean Names)</h2>
<p data-start="764" data-end="790">If there are extra spaces:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="792" data-end="842"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>=UPPER(TRIM(A2)) &amp; ". " &amp; PROPER(TRIM(B2))</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="844" data-end="855">👉 Ensures:</p>
<ul data-start="856" data-end="910">
<li data-section-id="b7fbfc" data-start="856" data-end="872">
<p data-start="858" data-end="872">H is capital</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1d862g6" data-start="873" data-end="890">
<p data-start="875" data-end="890">Ram is proper</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nhhy5g" data-start="891" data-end="910">
<p data-start="893" data-end="910">No extra spaces</p>
</li>
</ul>
