<hr data-start="313" data-end="316">
<h2 data-section-id="1h260ag" data-start="318" data-end="336">🎯 Short Answer</h2>
<p data-start="338" data-end="454">👉 <strong data-start="341" data-end="383">YES, you can do it without Power Pivot</strong><br data-start="383" data-end="386">
👉 But you will use <strong data-start="406" data-end="429">Power Query (merge)</strong> instead of relationships</p>
<hr data-start="456" data-end="459">
<h2 data-section-id="1klchv5" data-start="461" data-end="496">🧠 Think like this (very simple)</h2>
<p data-start="498" data-end="507">You have:</p>
<ul data-start="509" data-end="568">
<li data-section-id="pzzdju" data-start="509" data-end="536">
<p data-start="511" data-end="536">Table 1 → Sales data 📊</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12h361u" data-start="537" data-end="568">
<p data-start="539" data-end="568">Table 2 → Calendar table 📅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="570" data-end="590">👉 Both are separate</p>
<p data-start="592" data-end="635">To analyze:<br>
👉 You need to <strong data-start="619" data-end="635">combine them</strong></p>
<hr data-start="637" data-end="640">
<h1 data-section-id="ntm6hm" data-start="642" data-end="670">🔥 TWO WAYS TO JOIN TABLES</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="684664" data-start="672" data-end="720">🟢 Method 1: Power Pivot (Your sir used this)</h2>
<ul data-start="722" data-end="790">
<li data-section-id="dhsqw" data-start="722" data-end="745">
<p data-start="724" data-end="745">Create relationship</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="yunqm7" data-start="746" data-end="770">
<p data-start="748" data-end="770">Tables stay separate</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10c161" data-start="771" data-end="790">
<p data-start="773" data-end="790">Advanced method</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="792" data-end="795">
<h2 data-section-id="1eh9ev9" data-start="797" data-end="840">🔵 Method 2: Power Query (YOUR METHOD ✅)</h2>
<p data-start="842" data-end="872">👉 Merge tables into ONE table</p>
<hr data-start="874" data-end="877">
<h1 data-section-id="fi2oll" data-start="879" data-end="914">🧭 HOW YOU WILL DO (Step-by-step)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1rt21vo" data-start="916" data-end="946">🥇 Step 1: Open Power Query</h2>
<ul data-start="948" data-end="1008">
<li data-section-id="1we7vd1" data-start="948" data-end="980">
<p data-start="950" data-end="980">Data → Queries &amp; Connections</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="25vvcs" data-start="981" data-end="1008">
<p data-start="983" data-end="1008">Double click your table</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1010" data-end="1013">
<h2 data-section-id="79diil" data-start="1015" data-end="1042">🥈 Step 2: Merge Queries</h2>
<ol data-start="1044" data-end="1139">
<li data-section-id="d8o7pc" data-start="1044" data-end="1079">
<p data-start="1047" data-end="1079">Go to <strong data-start="1053" data-end="1077">Home → Merge Queries</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="398rbm" data-start="1080" data-end="1139">
<p data-start="1083" data-end="1090">Select:</p>
<ul data-start="1094" data-end="1139">
<li data-section-id="3y5nz1" data-start="1094" data-end="1113">
<p data-start="1096" data-end="1113">Table 1 → Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xaoa3o" data-start="1117" data-end="1139">
<p data-start="1119" data-end="1139">Table 2 → Calendar</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1141" data-end="1144">
<h2 data-section-id="1fvue62" data-start="1146" data-end="1180">🥉 Step 3: Select common column</h2>
<p data-start="1182" data-end="1193">👉 Usually:</p>
<ul data-start="1194" data-end="1248">
<li data-section-id="111n792" data-start="1194" data-end="1222">
<p data-start="1196" data-end="1222">Sales table → Order Date</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="147zghu" data-start="1223" data-end="1248">
<p data-start="1225" data-end="1248">Calendar table → Date</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1250" data-end="1271">👉 Click both columns</p>
<hr data-start="1273" data-end="1276">
<h2 data-section-id="1tzl17r" data-start="1278" data-end="1308">🏅 Step 4: Choose Join Type</h2>
<p data-start="1310" data-end="1351">👉 Use:<br>
<strong data-start="1318" data-end="1351">Left Outer Join (most common)</strong></p>
<p data-start="1353" data-end="1404">Meaning:<br>
👉 Keep all sales data + add calendar info</p>
<hr data-start="1406" data-end="1409">
<h2 data-section-id="k8ss3r" data-start="1411" data-end="1431">🥇 Step 5: Expand</h2>
<ul data-start="1433" data-end="1500">
<li data-section-id="1vb2vqj" data-start="1433" data-end="1454">
<p data-start="1435" data-end="1454">Click expand icon</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5wvcnf" data-start="1455" data-end="1500">
<p data-start="1457" data-end="1477">Select columns like:</p>
<ul data-start="1480" data-end="1500">
<li data-section-id="1372cig" data-start="1480" data-end="1489">
<p data-start="1482" data-end="1489">Month</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2dx3gn" data-start="1492" data-end="1500">
<p data-start="1494" data-end="1500">Year</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1502" data-end="1505">
<p data-start="1507" data-end="1541">👉 Now your tables are COMBINED 💥</p>
<hr data-start="1543" data-end="1546">
<h2 data-section-id="13f3d4j" data-start="1548" data-end="1566">🎯 Final Result</h2>
<p data-start="1568" data-end="1596">You now have ONE table like:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="1598" data-end="1659" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="1598" data-end="1629"><tr data-start="1598" data-end="1629"><th data-start="1598" data-end="1605" data-col-size="sm" class="">Date</th><th data-start="1605" data-end="1613" data-col-size="sm" class="">Sales</th><th data-start="1613" data-end="1621" data-col-size="sm" class="">Month</th><th data-start="1621" data-end="1629" data-col-size="sm" class="">Year</th></tr></thead></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="1661" data-end="1668">👉 Now:</p>
<ul data-start="1669" data-end="1729">
<li data-section-id="1fceb2" data-start="1669" data-end="1684">
<p data-start="1671" data-end="1684">Pivot works</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="imz1xk" data-start="1685" data-end="1703">
<p data-start="1687" data-end="1703">Analysis works</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n7pkq1" data-start="1704" data-end="1729">
<p data-start="1706" data-end="1729">No Power Pivot needed</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1731" data-end="1734">
<h1 data-section-id="oug6ag" data-start="1736" data-end="1761">⚠️ IMPORTANT DIFFERENCE</h1>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="1763" data-end="1956" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="1763" data-end="1798"><tr data-start="1763" data-end="1798"><th data-start="1763" data-end="1783" data-col-size="sm" class="">Power Query Merge</th><th data-start="1783" data-end="1798" data-col-size="sm" class="">Power Pivot</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="1833" data-end="1956"><tr data-start="1833" data-end="1882"><td data-start="1833" data-end="1857" data-col-size="sm">Combines into 1 table</td><td data-start="1857" data-end="1882" data-col-size="sm">Keeps tables separate</td></tr><tr data-start="1883" data-end="1909"><td data-start="1883" data-end="1892" data-col-size="sm">Easier</td><td data-start="1892" data-end="1909" data-col-size="sm">More advanced</td></tr><tr data-start="1910" data-end="1956"><td data-start="1910" data-end="1935" data-col-size="sm">Perfect for your level</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="1935" data-end="1956">Advanced modeling</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="1958" data-end="1961">
<h2 data-section-id="q6ptym" data-start="1963" data-end="1988">🔥 Best Choice for YOU</h2>
<p data-start="1990" data-end="2069">👉 Use <strong data-start="1997" data-end="2018">Power Query merge</strong><br data-start="2018" data-end="2021">
👉 This is already <strong data-start="2040" data-end="2069">strong enough for project</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2071" data-end="2074">
<h1 data-section-id="1vays5a" data-start="2076" data-end="2101">🎮 Simple Understanding</h1>
<p data-start="2103" data-end="2175">👉 Power Pivot = database style<br data-start="2134" data-end="2137">
👉 Power Query = combine and analyze</p>
<hr data-start="2177" data-end="2180">
<h2 data-section-id="alpzw3" data-start="2182" data-end="2200">⚡ Final Verdict</h2>
<p data-start="2202" data-end="2284">👉 ❌ You don’t NEED Power Pivot<br data-start="2233" data-end="2236">
👉 ✅ You can do full project using Power Query</p>
<hr data-start="2286" data-end="2289">
<h2 data-section-id="1x0hcb1" data-start="2291" data-end="2306">🚀 Next Step</h2>
<p data-start="2308" data-end="2322">After merging:</p>
<p data-start="2324" data-end="2363">👉 Load data → Create Pivot → Analyze</p>
<hr data-start="2365" data-end="2368">
<p data-start="2370" data-end="2489" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want next:<br>
👉 I can guide you <strong data-start="2407" data-end="2486">exactly what columns to select and how to merge step-by-step with your file</strong> 🔥</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary round