t="0" data-end="78">Alright 😄 I checked your file like a recruiter opening it for the first time.</p>
<h2 data-section-id="1crh185" data-start="80" data-end="105">🎯 Your Project Rating</h2>
<p data-start="107" data-end="167">👉 <strong data-start="110" data-end="122">7.5 / 10</strong> (GOOD… but not yet “can’t reject her” level)</p>
<hr data-start="169" data-end="172">
<h2 data-section-id="gx17n7" data-start="174" data-end="216">🧠 What you did WELL (Strong points 💪)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1qk1z9b" data-start="218" data-end="246">✅ 1. Real Dataset Choice</h3>
<ul data-start="247" data-end="320">
<li data-section-id="1h9zmta" data-start="247" data-end="320">
<p data-start="249" data-end="320">Hospital ER data = 🔥 very good domain<br data-start="287" data-end="290">
👉 Looks practical, not random</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="322" data-end="325">
<h3 data-section-id="k96ukm" data-start="327" data-end="361">✅ 2. Multiple Sheets Structure</h3>
<ul data-start="362" data-end="411">
