</li>
<li data-section-id="zun9ib" data-start="393" data-end="411">
<p data-start="395" data-end="411">Metrics sheets</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="413" data-end="454">👉 Shows you understand <strong data-start="437" data-end="454">analysis flow</strong></p>
<hr data-start="456" data-end="459">
<h3 data-section-id="u4eqk3" data-start="461" data-end="497">✅ 3. KPI Thinking (Good sign 🧠)</h3>
<ul data-start="498" data-end="552">
<li data-section-id="l1ip86" data-start="498" data-end="511">
<p data-start="500" data-end="511">Wait time</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="r2oo4k" data-start="512" data-end="534">
<p data-start="514" data-end="534">Satisfaction score</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cuvjh4" data-start="535" data-end="552">
<p data-start="537" data-end="552">Patient count</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="554" data-end="607">👉 You are thinking like analyst, not just Excel user</p>
<hr data-start="609" data-end="612">
<h3 data-section-id="c7ici0" data-start="614" data-end="634">✅ 4. Pivot Usage</h3>
<ul data-start="635" data-end="703">
<li data-section-id="11nyj52" data-start="635" data-end="703">
<p data-start="637" data-end="703">You used pivots properly<br data-start="661" data-end="664">
👉 This is expected and you did it well</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="705" data-end="708">
<h2 data-section-id="11rf6vo" data-start="710" data-end="751">⚠️ Where you LOST marks (Important 🚨)</h2>
<p data-start="753" data-end="784">This is why it's 7.5 and not 9+</p>
<hr data-start="786" data-end="789">
<h3 data-section-id="1nlpfcg" data-start="791" data-end="823">❌ 1. Dashboard Story is WEAK</h3>
<p data-start="825" data-end="885">Right now:<br>
👉 It shows numbers<br data-start="855" data-end="858">
But doesn’t clearly answer:</p>
<ul data-start="887" data-end="952">
<li data-section-id="1n451v0" data-start="887" data-end="918">
<p data-start="889" data-end="918">Is performance good or bad?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9pe796" data-start="919" data-end="952">
<p data-start="921" data-end="952">What should hospital improve?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="954" data-end="989">👉 Missing <strong data-start="965" data-end="989">clear business story</strong></p>
<hr data-start="991" data-end="994">
<h3 data-section-id="2wslxq" data-start="996" data-end="1029">❌ 2. Insights are NOT visible</h3>
<p data-start="1031" data-end="1054">Recruiter wants to SEE:</p>
<p data-start="1056" data-end="1081">👉 Written insights like:</p>
<ul data-start="1082" data-end="1190">
<li data-section-id="z6fvnk" data-start="1082" data-end="1138">
<p data-start="1084" data-end="1138">“Average wait time is high, indicating inefficiency”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bke89r" data-start="1139" data-end="1190">
<p data-start="1141" data-end="1190">“Patient satisfaction is low during peak hours”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1192" data-end="1239">👉 Your file = mostly visuals, less explanation</p>
<hr data-start="1241" data-end="1244">
<h3 data-section-id="ftci58" data-start="1246" data-end="1276">❌ 3. Design can be cleaner</h3>
