<hr data-start="1494" data-end="1497">
<h2 data-section-id="1s9veul" data-start="1499" data-end="1532">🔥 How to turn this into 9+/10</h2>
<p data-start="1534" data-end="1554">Do these upgrades 👇</p>
<hr data-start="1556" data-end="1559">
