</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1819" data-end="1850">👉 Instantly looks professional</p>
<hr data-start="1852" data-end="1855">
<h3 data-section-id="qjfvgp" data-start="1857" data-end="1885">💥 3. Add Comparison KPI</h3>
