ata-start="0" data-end="30">First, your corrected version:</p>
<p data-start="32" data-end="212"><strong data-start="32" data-end="212">“If I include many projects in one repository, should I create a README for each project, or only one README for the whole repository? Is it possible to have multiple READMEs?”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="214" data-end="217">
<h2 data-section-id="1h260ag" data-start="219" data-end="237">🎯 Short Answer</h2>
<p data-start="239" data-end="310">👉 <strong data-start="242" data-end="280">YES, you can have multiple READMEs</strong><br data-start="280" data-end="283">
👉 But use them <strong data-start="299" data-end="310">smartly</strong></p>
<hr data-start="312" data-end="315">
<h1 data-section-id="3eaw2j" data-start="317" data-end="359">🧠 Best Practice (What professionals do)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1d1ansy" data-start="361" data-end="386">✅ Structure like this:</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="388" data-end="568"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>📁 Data-Analysis-Projects</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── README.md  ← Main (important)</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── 📁 Project-1</span><br><span>│   └── README.md</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── 📁 Project-2</span><br><span>│   └── README.md</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── 📁 Project-3</span><br><span>│   └── README.md</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="570" data-end="573">
<h1 data-section-id="1svlnlj" data-start="575" data-end="601">🧭 What each README does</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="hlk36c" data-start="603" data-end="632">🏠 Main README (Top level)</h2>
<p data-start="634" data-end="672">👉 This is your <strong data-start="650" data-end="672">portfolio overview</strong></p>
<p data-start="674" data-end="692">It should include:</p>
<ul data-start="693" data-end="798">
<li data-section-id="1yle6li" data-start="693" data-end="706">
<p data-start="695" data-end="706">About you</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lwiriv" data-start="707" data-end="747">
<p data-start="709" data-end="747">Tools (Excel, SQL, Python, Power BI)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="7lu0o5" data-start="748" data-end="768">
<p data-start="750" data-end="768">List of projects</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16jrsmy" data-start="769" data-end="798">
<p data-start="771" data-end="798">Short description of each</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="800" data-end="832">👉 Think of it like <strong data-start="820" data-end="832">homepage</strong></p>
<hr data-start="834" data-end="837">
<h2 data-section-id="1skyjqp" data-start="839" data-end="880">📂 Project README (Inside each folder)</h2>
<p data-start="882" data-end="917">👉 This is <strong data-start="893" data-end="917">detailed explanation</strong></p>
<p data-start="919" data-end="927">Include:</p>
<ul data-start="928" data-end="1039">
<li data-section-id="lsttk6" data-start="928" data-end="949">
<p data-start="930" data-end="949">Problem statement</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rjllp0" data-start="950" data-end="966">
<p data-start="952" data-end="966">Dataset info</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gkvrb8" data-start="967" data-end="981">
<p data-start="969" data-end="981">Tools used</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hovsjd" data-start="982" data-end="1001">
<p data-start="984" data-end="1001">Steps performed</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="za9bul" data-start="1002" data-end="1014">
<p data-start="1004" data-end="1014">Insights</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qhjwg0" data-start="1015" data-end="1039">
<p data-start="1017" data-end="1039">Dashboard screenshot</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1041" data-end="1078">👉 Think of it like <strong data-start="1061" data-end="1078">project story</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1080" data-end="1083">
<h1 data-section-id="18gflr8" data-start="1085" data-end="1106">🔥 Why this is BEST</h1>
<p data-start="1108" data-end="1132">👉 Recruiter opens repo:</p>
<ol data-start="1134" data-end="1206">
<li data-section-id="1cj9mov" data-start="1134" data-end="1171">
<p data-start="1137" data-end="1171">Sees main README → gets overview</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1yo4thd" data-start="1172" data-end="1206">
<p data-start="1175" data-end="1206">Clicks project → sees details</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1208" data-end="1257">👉 Smooth experience = 💼 professional impression</p>
<hr data-start="1259" data-end="1262">
<h1 data-section-id="155tsn9" data-start="1264" data-end="1282">❌ What NOT to do</h1>
<ul data-start="1284" data-end="1376">
<li data-section-id="191x464" data-start="1284" data-end="1331">
<p data-start="1286" data-end="1331">Only 1 README with everything ❌ (too messy)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vhpdf1" data-start="1332" data-end="1376">
<p data-start="1334" data-end="1376">No README in projects ❌ (no explanation)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1378" data-end="1381">
<h1 data-section-id="f34602" data-start="1383" data-end="1401">🎯 Final Verdict</h1>
<p data-start="1403" data-end="1410">👉 Use:</p>
<ul data-start="1411" data-end="1459">
<li data-section-id="1154aaw" data-start="1411" data-end="1432">
<p data-start="1413" data-end="1432"><strong data-start="1413" data-end="1430">1 main README</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j9aej5" data-start="1433" data-end="1459">
<p data-start="1435" data-end="1459"><strong data-start="1435" data-end="1459">1 README per project</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1461" data-end="1491">👉 This is industry standard ✅</p>
<hr data-start="1493" data-end="1496">
<h1 data-section-id="1t1xb28" data-start="1498" data-end="1525">🚀 Pro Tip (Game changer)</h1>
<p data-start="1527" data-end="1542">In main README:</p>
<p data-start="1544" data-end="1567">👉 Add clickable links:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1569" data-end="1624"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>🔹 Hospital ER Dashboard → [View Project](link)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1626" data-end="1660">👉 Makes your repo look 🔥 premium</p>
