<p data-start="32" data-end="200"><strong data-start="32" data-end="200">“Now it’s time for LinkedIn. I am a B.Com graduate and want to become a data analyst. You already know my skills, so let’s set up my LinkedIn profile from scratch.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="202" data-end="205">
<p data-start="207" data-end="352">Alright. Now we build your <strong data-start="234" data-end="268">LinkedIn like a personal brand</strong>, not just a profile 💼✨<br data-start="292" data-end="295">
Think of it as your <strong data-start="315" data-end="352">digital resume + first impression</strong></p>
<hr data-start="354" data-end="357">
<h1 data-section-id="1q48mry" data-start="359" data-end="392">🎯 1. HEADLINE (Most Important)</h1>
<p data-start="394" data-end="437">This appears everywhere. It must be strong.</p>
<h2 data-section-id="y31n3t" data-start="439" data-end="467">🔥 Best Headline for YOU:</h2>
<p data-start="469" data-end="568"><strong data-start="469" data-end="568">“Aspiring Data Analyst | Excel • SQL • Power BI • Python | Turning Data into Business Insights”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="570" data-end="573">
<p data-start="575" data-end="593">👉 Why this works:</p>
<ul data-start="594" data-end="666">
<li data-section-id="fn7wk9" data-start="594" data-end="623">
<p data-start="596" data-end="623">Clear goal (Data Analyst)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uxhss3" data-start="624" data-end="639">
<p data-start="626" data-end="639">Shows tools</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dyiokg" data-start="640" data-end="666">
<p data-start="642" data-end="666">Shows mindset (insights)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="668" data-end="671">
<h1 data-section-id="1015az7" data-start="673" data-end="707">🧠 2. ABOUT SECTION (Your Story)</h1>
<p data-start="709" data-end="750">Copy this 👇 (this is customized for YOU)</p>
<div class="relative w-full"><div id="writing-block-9044ac81-cdf1-45b7-8bcf-275f13739f1c" class="group relative my-4 w-full overflow-visible rounded-[24px] bg-token-bg-primary dark:bg-[#2a2a2a] shadow-[0px_0px_0px_1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07),0px_4px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02)]" data-writing-block="true" data-testid="writing-block-container"><div class="z-1 md:sticky top-(--sticky-padding-top) bg-token-bg-primary dark:bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-t-[24px]" data-testid="writing-block-header-sticky-container"><div class="bg-token-bg-primary flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-3 font-sans dark:bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-t-[24px] py-2.5" data-testid="writing-block-header-surface" style="padding-left: calc(5 * var(--spacing)); padding-right: calc(2 * var(--spacing));"><div class="flex grow gap-3 items-center"><div class="text-token-text-tertiary flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 grow cursor-default items-center self-center text-sm font-medium"><div class="truncate">Writing</div></div></div><div class="flex shrink-0 items-center"><div><div class="flex items-center"><button class="gap-1 select-none text-sm font-medium text-token-text-primary hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary flex size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full p-1.5 transition-colors" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div><div class="writing-block-editor markdown-new-styling relative flow-root pt-(--writing-block-editor-pt) pe-(--writing-block-editor-pr) pb-(--writing-block-editor-pb) ps-(--writing-block-editor-pl)" style="--writing-block-editor-pt: 0px; --writing-block-editor-pr: calc(5 * var(--spacing)); --writing-block-editor-pb: calc(4 * var(--spacing)); --writing-block-editor-pl: calc(5 * var(--spacing));"><div class="ProseMirror markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full min-h-6 break-words focus:outline-none" contenteditable="true" aria-disabled="false" dir="auto" translate="no"><p><span>I am a B.Com graduate with a strong interest in data analysis and problem-solving.</span></p><p><span>I have developed skills in Excel, SQL, Power BI, and Python, and I enjoy working with data to uncover patterns, trends, and insights that can support better decision-making.</span></p><p><span>I have built end-to-end data analysis projects involving data cleaning, transformation (Power Query), analysis using Pivot Tables and SQL, and dashboard creation. My projects focus on real-world scenarios such as sales performance and hospital data analysis.</span></p><p><span>I am currently looking for opportunities where I can apply my skills, continue learning, and grow as a data analyst.</span></p><p><span>Skills: Excel | Power Query | SQL | Python | Power BI | Data Analysis | Dashboarding</span></p></div></div></div></div>
