<h2 data-section-id="1h24mor" data-start="74" data-end="106">🎯 What is “Bio” on LinkedIn?</h2>
<p data-start="108" data-end="204">👉 It’s your <strong data-start="121" data-end="154">About section (short version)</strong><br data-start="154" data-end="157">
👉 3–5 lines that make recruiter stop and think</p>
