-b232-472b-ac7a-ff4b87a9075b" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="31">First, your corrected sentence:</p>
<p data-start="33" data-end="181"><strong data-start="33" data-end="181">“First, I will create a folder and upload the README file, then my PowerPoint presentation, then my dashboard file, and then the raw data file.”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="183" data-end="186">
<h2 data-section-id="1swqdw1" data-start="188" data-end="245">🎯 Yes… but let’s make it PROFESSIONAL (small upgrade)</h2>
<p data-start="247" data-end="322">Your idea is correct ✅<br data-start="269" data-end="272">
But order + structure matters a LOT for recruiters</p>
<hr data-start="324" data-end="327">
<h1 data-section-id="vqfdhm" data-start="329" data-end="362">🔥 DO IT LIKE THIS (BEST ORDER)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="iufulz" data-start="364" data-end="391">🥇 Step 1: Create Folder</h2>
<p data-start="393" data-end="407">Name it clean:</p>
<p data-start="409" data-end="435">👉 <code data-start="412" data-end="435">Hospital-ER-Dashboard</code></p>
<hr data-start="437" data-end="440">
<h2 data-section-id="4bblt6" data-start="442" data-end="488">🥈 Step 2: Inside folder, create subfolders</h2>
<p data-start="490" data-end="548">Don’t dump everything in one place ❌<br data-start="526" data-end="529">
Organize like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="550" data-end="650"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Hospital-ER-Dashboard</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── README.md</span><br><span>├── 📁 Data</span><br><span>├── 📁 Presentation</span><br><span>├── 📁 Images</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="652" data-end="655">
<h2 data-section-id="14v7nj7" data-start="657" data-end="698">🥉 Step 3: Upload files in RIGHT place</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1m1544a" data-start="700" data-end="716">📄 1. README</h3>
<p data-start="717" data-end="751">👉 Put directly inside main folder</p>
<hr data-start="753" data-end="756">
<h3 data-section-id="15siwj3" data-start="758" data-end="782">📊 2. Dashboard file</h3>
<p data-start="783" data-end="839">👉 Put in main folder<br data-start="804" data-end="807">
(very important, easy to access)</p>
<hr data-start="841" data-end="844">
