<h2 data-section-id="1bqrkp1" data-start="173" data-end="194">🎯 Do this EXACTLY</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="obb7sd" data-start="196" data-end="209">1. Click:</h3>
<p data-start="210" data-end="240">👉 <strong data-start="213" data-end="240">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
<hr data-start="242" data-end="245">
<h3 data-section-id="1alc6s6" data-start="247" data-end="285">2. Drag &amp; drop your dashboard file</h3>
<p data-start="287" data-end="323">👉 Your Excel file (the <code data-start="311" data-end="318">.xlsm</code> one)</p>
<hr data-start="325" data-end="328">
<h3 data-section-id="ti6p86" data-start="330" data-end="364">3. IMPORTANT (Don’t miss this)</h3>
<p data-start="366" data-end="403">At the top you’ll see file path like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="405" data-end="436"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Data-Analysis-Projects/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="438" data-end="454">👉 Change it to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="456" data-end="506"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Hospital-ER-Analysis-Dashboard/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="508" data-end="511">
<h3 data-section-id="cfgzi9" data-start="513" data-end="524">🧠 Why?</h3>
<p data-start="526" data-end="590">👉 So your file goes inside your project folder<br data-start="573" data-end="576">
👉 Not outside</p>
<hr data-start="592" data-end="595">
