<hr data-start="70" data-end="73">
<h2 data-section-id="1h260ag" data-start="75" data-end="93">🎯 Short Answer</h2>
<p data-start="95" data-end="162">👉 <strong data-start="98" data-end="162">YES — and it’s actually the BEST way (professional way) 💼🔥</strong></p>
<hr data-start="164" data-end="167">
<h2 data-section-id="p9rtl2" data-start="169" data-end="198">🧠 Why CMD (Git) is better</h2>
<ul data-start="200" data-end="274">
<li data-section-id="1kqnk0u" data-start="200" data-end="212">
<p data-start="202" data-end="212">Faster ⚡</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fk6ecc" data-start="213" data-end="229">
<p data-start="215" data-end="229">Full control</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="yzb4s7" data-start="230" data-end="252">
<p data-start="232" data-end="252">Looks professional</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1g1hxxi" data-start="253" data-end="274">
<p data-start="255" data-end="274">Used in real jobs</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="276" data-end="340">👉 Recruiter won’t see how you uploaded, but YOU become stronger</p>
<hr data-start="342" data-end="345">
<h1 data-section-id="j2olws" data-start="347" data-end="395">🚀 If you want to use CMD, follow this EXACTLY</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="162evzv" data-start="397" data-end="419">🥇 Step 1: Open CMD</h2>
