 I clearly understand your situation.</p>
<hr data-start="52" data-end="55">
<h2 data-section-id="16aj0q0" data-start="57" data-end="85">🎯 Your current situation</h2>
<ul data-start="87" data-end="188">
<li data-section-id="185up9w" data-start="87" data-end="141">
<p data-start="89" data-end="141">✅ Folder + README → already on <strong data-start="120" data-end="139">GitHub (online)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mbzxuv" data-start="142" data-end="188">
<p data-start="144" data-end="188">❌ Files → still on your <strong data-start="168" data-end="186">laptop (local)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="190" data-end="263">👉 So now you want to <strong data-start="212" data-end="263">send (upload) your laptop files → GitHub folder</strong></p>
<hr data-start="265" data-end="268">
<h2 data-section-id="17bakb8" data-start="270" data-end="305">⚠️ Important (very simple truth)</h2>
<p data-start="307" data-end="332">👉 CMD method works when:</p>
<ul data-start="333" data-end="361">
<li data-section-id="1gayel" data-start="333" data-end="361">
<p data-start="335" data-end="361">Repo is on your computer</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="363" data-end="404">👉 BUT your repo is only online right now</p>
<p data-start="406" data-end="462">So first we must <strong data-start="423" data-end="462">bring repo to your computer (clone)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="464" data-end="467">
<h1 data-section-id="1azflw2" data-start="469" data-end="522">🥇 STEP 1 — Clone your GitHub repo to your computer</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="2hwm3q" data-start="524" data-end="538">👉 Do this:</h2>
<ol data-start="540" data-end="600">
<li data-section-id="uvqg2g" data-start="540" data-end="577">
<p data-start="543" data-end="577">Go to your GitHub repo (browser)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="eqru0w" data-start="578" data-end="600">
<p data-start="581" data-end="600">Click green button:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="602" data-end="613">👉 <strong data-start="605" data-end="613">Code</strong></p>
<ol start="3" data-start="615" data-end="639">
<li data-section-id="7yigha" data-start="615" data-end="639">
<p data-start="618" data-end="639">Copy the link (HTTPS)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="641" data-end="644">
<h2 data-section-id="eh82zp" data-start="646" data-end="673">🧭 Now open CMD anywhere</h2>
<p data-start="675" data-end="685">Then type:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="687" data-end="718"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼs">git</span><span> clone YOUR_LINK</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="720" data-end="731">👉 Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="732" data-end="795"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div