<hr data-start="797" data-end="800">
<h2 data-section-id="idxicn" data-start="802" data-end="822">🎯 What this does</h2>
<p data-start="824" data-end="925">👉 Creates a folder on your computer<br data-start="860" data-end="863">
👉 Same as your GitHub repo<br data-start="890" data-end="893">
👉 Includes your README + folder</p>
<hr data-start="927" data-end="930">
<h2 data-section-id="ly5sx8" data-start="932" data-end="963">🥈 STEP 2 — Open that folder</h2>
<p data-start="965" data-end="979">After cloning:</p>
<ol data-start="981" data-end="1089">
<li data-section-id="ktg8x6" data-start="981" data-end="1007">
