</li>
<li data-section-id="9pkyq8" data-start="1008" data-end="1020">
<p data-start="1011" data-end="1020">Open it</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1c9dbpb" data-start="1021" data-end="1089">
<p data-start="1024" data-end="1037">You will see:</p>
<ul data-start="1041" data-end="1089">
<li data-section-id="14f9mx" data-start="1041" data-end="1062">
<p data-start="1043" data-end="1062">Your GitHub files</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18276wq" data-start="1066" data-end="1089">
<p data-start="1068" data-end="1089">Your project folder</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1091" data-end="1094">
<h2 data-section-id="ag0dji" data-start="1096" data-end="1132">🥉 STEP 3 — Put your files inside</h2>
<p data-start="1134" data-end="1138">Now:</p>
<p data-start="1140" data-end="1161">👉 Copy your 3 files:</p>
<ul data-start="1162" data-end="1191">
<li data-section-id="1lb2ur0" data-start="1162" data-end="1175">
<p data-start="1164" data-end="1175">Dashboard</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16x0pu6" data-start="1176" data-end="1183">
